{"type":"message","id":"8f31614a","parentId":"3688aca1","timestamp":"2026-06-30T21:43:03.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我继续执行任务。备份完成。现在需要按顺序执行7项任务：\n\n1. ptz_controller.py瘦身（需验证）\n2. 合并两个Orchestrator（需确认）\n3. 统一WS Manager（需验证是否可简化）\n4. SADP处理（需确认）\n5. 更新Logger命名区分\n6. 清理log/日志\n7. 清理data/冗余\n\n用户说\"执行1、2、3（需验证是否可以简化）、4（需确认后再操作）\"，这意味着1和2可以直接执行，3和4需要先验证。\n\n让我先执行简单的（6、7），然后再处理需要验证的（1-5）。\n\n先从任务6开始：清理log/ 3天前的日志。当前是2026-07-01，3天前是2026-06-28。所以删除6月27日及之前的.md日志文件。\n\n然后任务7：删除data/的3个空子目录（calibration/, db/, hls/）\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"备份完成。开始执行。先做安全删除（任务6、7），再做验证重构（1-5）。\n\n## 任务6：清理 log/ 日志（保留3天）\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c461fc399cb843009e43af0b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os, re\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nlog_dir = Path('log')\ncutoff = datetime.now() - timedelta(days=3)  # 3天前\ndeleted = 0\ntotal_size = 0\n\nfor f in log_dir.glob('*.md'):\n    # 解析日期: log_20260624-001.md\n    m = re.match(r'log_(\\d{8})', f.name)\n    if m:\n        file_date = datetime.strptime(m.group(1), '%Y%m%d')\n        if file_date < cutoff:\n            size = f.stat().st_size\n            total_size += size\n            f.unlink()\n            deleted += 1\n            print(f'  DEL: {f.name} ({size/1024/1024:.1f}MB)')\n\nprint(f'\\n删除: {deleted} 个文件, 释放: {total_size/1024/1024:.1f}MB')\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":564,"cacheRead":65072,"cacheWrite":2707,"totalTokens":68349,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782855771252,"responseId":"msg_5947fef0-d6c7-4199-b250-4e4678736685"}}
