hese are different loggers for different purposes\n\nActually, let me re-think the approach. The user wants:\n1. ptz_controller.py slimming - remove duplicate classes, import from standalone\n2. Merge Orchestrators\n3. Unify WS Manager\n4. Handle SADP\n5. Logger naming distinction\n\nFor task 1, the duplicate classes in ptz_controller.py that can be replaced:\n- Logger → use ptz/core/logger.py's LOG instead\n- ConfigManager → check if there's a standalone version\n- SADPDevice → check\n- ISAPIResponse, ISAPIClient → check ptz/isapi/client.py\n\nBut first, I MUST restore ptz/core/logger.py which was incorrectly deleted.\n\nLet me proceed step by step:\n1. First restore ptz/core/logger.py\n2. Then analyze ptz_controller.py more thoroughly\n3. Continue with other tasks","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"继续推进。先确认一个关键问题——之前删除的 `ptz/core/logger.py` 是否被其他文件引用：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d216ea2a079a422d85181641","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; Get-ChildItem -Path \"src\" -Recurse -File -Filter \"*.py\" | Select-String -Pattern \"from src\\.ptz\\.core\\.logger import|from \\.core\\.logger import|from \\.\\.core\\.logger import|ptz\\.core\\.logger\" | Select-Object Filename, Line | Format-Table -AutoSize","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1861,"cacheRead":71108,"cacheWrite":5400,"totalTokens":78375,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782855813337,"responseId":"msg_7c1d9196-74a8-4923-bfe5-598ee0350741"}}
