{"type":"message","id":"c7150365","parentId":"732ce940","timestamp":"2026-06-30T21:50:40.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要继续执行清理任务。当前进度：\n\n已完成：\n- 任务5：Logger命名区分 ✅\n- 任务6：清理log/ ✅  \n- 任务7：清理data/空目录 ✅\n- 任务1部分：ptz_controller.py中删除了内嵌Logger，改为import ✅\n\n待完成：\n- 任务1：需要在client.py补充capture_picture()和_get_binary()，然后删除ptz_controller.py内嵌的ISAPIResponse和ISAPIClient\n- 任务2：重命名两个Orchestrator\n- 任务3：WS Manager验证\n- 任务4：SADP确认\n- 版本号更新到8.01\n- 重启测试\n\n现在我在读取client.py的末尾，需要在ISAPIClient类中添加capture_picture()和_get_binary()方法。从读取结果看，文件在第257行结束，最后一个方法是get_xml_float()。\n\n我需要在get_xml_float()方法后面添加：\n1. _get_binary()方法 - 获取二进制响应\n2. capture_picture()方法 - 截图\n\n让我继续执行。\n在 `client.py` 末尾添加截图和二进制获取方法：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7e1bb9ca80cd4198a254bb36","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def get_xml_float(self, root: ET.Element, tag: str, default: float = 0.0) -> float:\n        \"\"\"从 XML 元素中安全提取浮点数。\"\"\"\n        text = self.get_xml_text(root, tag, str(default))\n        try:\n            return float(text)\n        except (ValueError, TypeError):\n            return default\n\n    def _get_binary(self, endpoint: str, timeout: int = 15) -> bytes | None:\n        \"\"\"从 ISAPI 端点获取二进制数据（截图、录像等）。\n\n        Args:\n            endpoint: ISAPI 端点路径\n            timeout: 超时秒数\n\n        Returns:\n            二进制数据，失败返回 None\n        \"\"\"\n        url = f\"{self.base_url}{endpoint}\"\n        LOG.log(\"info\", f\"ISAPI binary GET: {endpoint}\")\n        try:\n            response = self.session.get(url, timeout=timeout)\n            if response.status_code == 200:\n                LOG.log(\"done\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 成功: {endpoint} ({len(response.content)} bytes)\")\n                return response.content\n            else:\n                LOG.log(\"error\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 失败: {endpoint} (HTTP {response.status_code})\")\n                return None\n        except requests.exceptions.Timeout:\n            LOG.log(\"error\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 超时: {endpoint}\")\n            return None\n        except requests.exceptions.ConnectionError as e:\n            LOG.log(\"error\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 连接失败: {endpoint} - {e}\")\n            return None\n        except Exception as e:\n            LOG.log(\"error\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 异常: {endpoint} - {e}\")\n            return None\n\n    def capture_picture(self, channel: int = 1) -> bytes | None:\n        \"\"\"从摄像头抓取 JPEG 图片。\n\n        Args:\n            channel: 通道号，默认 1\n\n        Returns:\n            JPEG 图片二进制数据，失败返回 None\n        \"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/Streaming/channels/{channel}01/picture\"\n        return self._get_binary(endpoint)","oldText":"    def get_xml_float(self, root: ET.Element, tag: str, default: float = 0.0) -> float:\n        \"\"\"从 XML 元素中安全提取浮点数。\"\"\"\n        text = self.get_xml_text(root, tag, str(default))\n        try:\n            return float(text)\n        except (ValueError, TypeError):\n            return default"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\ptz\\isapi\\client.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nNow I need to add the `capture_picture()` and `_get_binary()` methods to `src/ptz/isapi/client.py`. Let me add them at the end of the ISAPIClient class.\n在 `src/ptz/isapi/client.py` 的 `ISAPIClient` 类末尾添加方法：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_81eb499df2054dbab7817f37","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def get_xml_float(self, root: ET.Element, tag: str, default: float = 0.0) -> float:\n        \"\"\"从 XML 元素中安全提取浮点数。\"\"\"\n        text = self.get_xml_text(root, tag, str(default))\n        try:\n            return float(text)\n        except (ValueError, TypeError):\n            return default\n\n    # ================================================================\n    #  二进制响应（截图 / 录像下载）— v8.01 从 ptz_controller.py 迁移\n    # ================================================================\n\n    def _get_binary(self, endpoint: str) -> bytes | None:\n        \"\"\"从 ISAPI 端点获取二进制响应（用于图片 / 视频文件）。\"\"\"\n        url = f\"{self.base_url}{endpoint}\"\n        LOG.log(\"info\", f\"ISAPI BINARY GET: {endpoint}\")\n        try:\n            response = self.session.get(url, timeout=15)\n            if response.status_code == 200:\n                return response.content\n            LOG.log(\"error\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 失败: {endpoint} (status={response.status_code})\")\n            return None\n        except requests.exceptions.Timeout:\n            LOG.log(\"error\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 超时: {endpoint}\")\n            return None\n        except Exception as e:\n            LOG.log(\"error\", f\"ISAPI binary GET 错误: {endpoint}: {e}\")\n            return None\n\n    def capture_picture(self, channel: int = 1) -> bytes | None:\n        \"\"\"通过 ISAPI 直接从摄像头抓取 JPEG 图片。\n\n        使用: GET /Streaming/Channels/{channel}/picture\n        \"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/Streaming/Channels/{channel}/picture\"\n        return self._get_binary(endpoint)","oldText":"    def get_xml_float(self, root: ET.Element, tag: str, default: float = 0.0) -> float:\n        \"\"\"从 XML 元素中安全提取浮点数。\"\"\"\n        text = self.get_xml_text(root, tag, str(default))\n        try:\n            return float(text)\n        except (ValueError, TypeError):\n            return default"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\ptz\\isapi\\client.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1569,"cacheRead":138737,"cacheWrite":724,"totalTokens":141036,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782856207373,"responseId":"msg_8ba33265-3db7-4a8a-8564-8d9e8fae7563"}}
