=========================================` then `class PTZDeviceController:`\n\nSo I need to replace everything from the `# ISAPI Client` section header to just before the `class PTZDeviceController:` separator.\n\nLet me construct the edit carefully. The old text should be:\n```\n# ============================================================\n# ISAPI Client\n# ============================================================\n\n@dataclass\nclass ISAPIResponse:\n... (all the ISAPIResponse and ISAPIClient code)\n        endpoint = f\"/Streaming/Channels/{channel}/picture\"\n        return self._get_binary(endpoint)\n\n```\n\nAnd the new text should just be the import (but the import needs to go at the top of the file with other imports).\n\nActually, I should:\n1. Add the import at the top of the file with other imports\n2. Delete the entire embedded ISAPI section\n\nLet me do this in two edits or use Python to do it more precisely.\n\nActually, for a large deletion like this (240+ lines), it's better to use a script. Let me write a Python script to:\n1. Add the import\n2. Delete the embedded classes\n找到边界了。第 613-857 行是内嵌的 ISAPI Client 代码（约 245 行）。需要删除并添加 import。\n\n由于这是一个很大的删除操作，我用 Python 脚本来精确处理：\n这个块太大了（~245行），用 Python 脚本精确处理：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3e0207ccc9d242c8bad83a3d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport re\n\nwith open('src/core/ptz_controller.py', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 找到 ISAPI Client section 的起始位置\n# 在 '# ISAPI Client' section 之前有一个分隔线\nisapi_section_start = content.find('# ============================================================\\n# ISAPI Client')\nif isapi_section_start == -1:\n    print('ERROR: Cannot find ISAPI Client section start')\n    exit(1)\n\n# 找到 PTZDeviceController class 前的分隔线\n# 在 capture_picture 方法之后\nptz_controller_marker = '\\n# ============================================================\\nclass PTZDeviceController:'\nisapi_section_end = content.find(ptz_controller_marker, isapi_section_start)\nif isapi_section_end == -1:\n    print('ERROR: Cannot find PTZDeviceController section')\n    exit(1)\n\n# 计算要删除的内容\nold_section = content[isapi_section_start:isapi_section_end]\nprint(f'Found ISAPI section: {len(old_section)} chars, lines ~{content[:isapi_section_start].count(chr(10))+1}-{content[:isapi_section_end].count(chr(10))+1}')\n\n# 替换为空（删除整个 section）\nnew_content = content[:isapi_section_start] + content[isapi_section_end:]\n\n# 在文件顶部的 import 区域添加 ISAPIClient 和 ISAPIResponse 的 import\n# 找到 'from src.ptz.isapi.ptz import PTZController' 这行，在它后面添加\nimport_line = 'from src.ptz.isapi.ptz import PTZController'\nnew_import = 'from src.ptz.isapi.client import ISAPIClient, ISAPIResponse'\nif new_import not in new_content:\n    new_content = new_content.replace(\n        import_line,\n        import_line + '\\n' + new_import\n    )\n    print(f'Added import: {new_import}')\n\nwith open('src/core/ptz_controller.py', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(new_content)\n\nprint('SUCCESS: Removed embedded ISAPIResponse + ISAPIClient, added import')\nprint(f'File size: {len(content)} -> {len(new_content)} chars (removed {len(content)-len(new_content)} chars)')\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":207,"output":3086,"cacheRead":125600,"cacheWrite":1794,"totalTokens":130687,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782856555100,"responseId":"msg_d220b646-b0d0-45ea-a282-70909b71f140"}}
