{"type":"message","id":"88c4d34d","parentId":"99a1db29","timestamp":"2026-06-30T22:08:05.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我继续执行任务。\n\n从上下文来看：\n- router.py 第 252 行的 \"orchestrator\" 是一个字符串，出现在 `module_keys` 列表中\n- 这个列表是用来检查各个模块的健康状态的\n\n这个 \"orchestrator\" 字符串是模块的键名，用于检查 `_managers` 字典中是否有对应的模块。现在 Orchestrator 已经被重命名为 TaskScheduler，但这里使用的字符串键名可能仍然需要保持为 \"orchestrator\"（取决于 `_managers` 字典中实际使用的键）。\n\n让我检查一下 `_managers` 字典中是如何存储模块的，以及 Orchestrator/TaskScheduler 是用什么键名存入的。\n\n不过，这个字符串键名 \"orchestrator\" 不需要更新为 \"task_scheduler\"，因为：\n1. 这是一个模块标识符，不是类名引用\n2. 如果 `_managers` 字典中使用 \"orchestrator\" 作为键来存储 TaskScheduler 实例，那么这个字符串应该保持一致\n\n实际上，我应该检查 router.py 中是否有地方将 Orchestrator 存入 `_managers` 字典，以及使用的键名是什么。\n\n让我搜索一下 router.py 中 \"orchestrator\" 字符串的所有使用，看看是否有地方需要更新。\n\n但实际上，更简单的做法是：这个字符串是模块标识符，不需要和类名保持一致。比如 \"device_manager\" 键存储的可能是 DeviceManager 类，但键名是不同的。所以这个 \"orchestrator\" 字符串可能不需要改。\n\n不过，我应该确认一下 router.py 中是否有地方用 \"orchestrator\" 键存储 TaskScheduler 实例。\n\n让我继续其他任务（任务3 WS Manager、任务4 SADP），然后更新版本号和重启测试。\n\n任务进度：\n1. ✅ 任务1：ptz_controller.py 瘦身完成\n2. ✅ 任务2：Orchestrator 重命名完成（TaskScheduler）\n3. 任务3：WS Manager 验证\n4. 任务4：SADP 处理\n5. 更新版本号\n6. 重启测试\n\n继续执行任务3和4。\n\n任务3：WS Manager\n之前分析过：\n- src/core/ws_manager.py 有 WebSocketManager 类\n- src/websocket/core/ws_manager.py 有 WSManager 类\n- 两个类名不同，但功能可能有重叠\n\n用户要求\"验证是否可以简化\"。让我检查这两个文件的内容。\n\n任务4：SADP\n之前分析过：\n- src/core/sadp_discovery.py 有 SADPManager（DLL 封装）\n- src/ptz/sadp/discovery.py 有纯 Python 多播实现\n- src/ptz/sadp/ 目录可能是旧实现\n\n需要确认 src/ptz/sadp/ 是否可以删除。\n\n让我先验证 WS Manager 的关系，然后处理 SADP。用户让我继续。从上下文看：\n\n1. router.py 第 252 行的 `\"orchestrator\"` 是一个字符串常量（模块键名），不是对 Orchestrator 类的直接引用。这是一个模块标识符，用于在 `_managers` 字典中查找模块状态，不需要更新为 \"task_scheduler\"。\n\n2. 现在需要继续执行：\n   - 任务3: WS Manager 验证简化\n   - 任务4: SADP 处理\n   - 更新版本号\n   - 重启测试\n\n让我继续执行这些任务。第 252 行的 `\"orchestrator\"` 是模块标识符字符串，用于 `_managers` 字典的键，不需要更新。\n\n继续任务3（WS Manager）和任务4（SADP）。先验证 WS Manager 是否可以简化：","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0487ed4fe51f4a2e9177d358de50f15e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ws_manager.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-6b4c6210fe6b4be9b375bde1444218ce","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; Get-ChildItem -Path \"src\\ptz\\sadp\" -Recurse -File -Filter \"*.py\" | Select-Object FullName, Length | Format-Table -AutoSize","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":127114,"output":880,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782857239484,"responseId":"cht000d8842@dx19f1a929a5529bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ab0a242","parentId":"88c4d34d","timestamp":"2026-06-30T22:08:06.356Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-0487ed4fe51f4a2e9177d358de50f15e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"WebSocket 连接管理器 - 线程安全的异步 WebSocket 管理。\"\"\"\n\nimport asyncio\nfrom typing import Any\n\n\nclass WebSocketManager:\n    \"\"\"管理 WebSocket 连接、频道订阅和消息分发。\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self) -> None:\n        self._clients: dict[str, Any] = {}\n        self._channels: dict[str, set[str]] = {}\n        self._lock = asyncio.Lock()\n\n    async def connect(self, ws: Any, client_id: str, channels: list[str] | None = None) -> None:\n        \"\"\"建立 WebSocket 连接并可选订阅频道。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            self._clients[client_id] = {\n                \"ws\": ws,\n                \"channels\": set(channels) if channels else set(),\n                \"connected_at\": asyncio.get_event_loop().time(),\n            }\n            for ch in channels or []:\n                self._channels.setdefault(ch, set()).add(client_id)\n\n    async def disconnect(self, client_id: str) -> None:\n        \"\"\"断开指定客户端连接并清理订阅。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            client = self._clients.pop(client_id, None)\n            if client:\n                for ch in client[\"channels\"]:\n                    self._channels.get(ch, set()).discard(client_id)\n                    if not self._channels[ch]:\n                        del self._channels[ch]\n\n    async def send_to(self, client_id: str, message: dict[str, Any]) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"发送消息给单个客户端。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            client = self._clients.get(client_id)\n            if not client:\n                return False\n        try:\n            await client[\"ws\"].send_json(message)\n            return True\n        except Exception:\n            await self.disconnect(client_id)\n            return False\n\n    async def broadcast(self, message: dict[str, Any], channel: str | None = None) -> int:\n        \"\"\"广播消息到所有客户端或指定频道。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            targets = (\n                {cid for cid in self._channels.get(channel, set()) if cid in self._clients}\n                if channel\n                else dict(self._clients)\n            )\n\n        sent = 0\n        failed = []\n        for cid in targets:\n            try:\n                await self._clients[cid][\"ws\"].send_json(message)\n                sent += 1\n            except Exception:\n                failed.append(cid)\n\n        async with self._lock:\n            for cid in failed:\n                await self.disconnect(cid)\n        return sent\n\n    async def subscribe(self, client_id: str, channel: str) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"订阅指定频道。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            client = self._clients.get(client_id)\n            if not client:\n                return False\n            client[\"channels\"].add(channel)\n            self._channels.setdefault(channel, set()).add(client_id)\n            return True\n\n    async def unsubscribe(self, client_id: str, channel: str) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"取消订阅指定频道。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            client = self._clients.get(client_id)\n            if not client:\n                return False\n            client[\"channels\"].discard(channel)\n            self._channels.get(channel, set()).discard(client_id)\n            if not self._channels.get(channel):\n                self._channels.pop(channel, None)\n            return True\n\n    async def get_client_count(self) -> int:\n        \"\"\"返回在线客户端数量。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            return len(self._clients)\n\n    async def get_client_info(self, client_id: str) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n        \"\"\"返回指定客户端信息。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            client = self._clients.get(client_id)\n            if not client:\n                return None\n            return {\n                \"client_id\": client_id,\n                \"channels\": list(client[\"channels\"]),\n                \"connected_at\": client[\"connected_at\"],\n            }\n\n    async def get_channel_stats(self) -> dict[str, int]:\n        \"\"\"返回各频道的订阅统计。\"\"\"\n        async with self._lock:\n            return {ch: len(members) for ch, members in self._channels.items()}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782857286356}}
