{"type":"message","id":"41224764","parentId":"bc51a02f","timestamp":"2026-06-30T22:08:22.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me read the src/websocket/core/ws_manager.py to understand the differences and verify if they can be simplified/unified.\n\nThe two WS Managers are:\n1. `src/core/ws_manager.py` - `WebSocketManager` (simple, 105 lines) - manages WebSocket connections with channel subscriptions\n2. `src/websocket/core/ws_manager.py` - `WSManager` (11.1KB) - more complex, with WSConnection, connection monitoring, heartbeat, etc.\n\nLet me also check if `src/ptz/sadp/` directory exists - the previous query returned no output, which means either:\n1. The directory doesn't exist\n2. The directory is empty\n\nLet me check.\nLet me also read the websocket/core/ws_manager.py to compare.\nWS Manager 分析完成。两个 WS Manager 功能不同：\n- `src/core/ws_manager.py` (`WebSocketManager`) — 简单的连接管理+频道订阅（router.py 用于 API 层推送）\n- `src/websocket/core/ws_manager.py` (`WSManager`) — 完整的 WebSocket 服务器（连接监控、心跳、认证）\n\n**结论**：两者是不同层次，`WebSocketManager` 是 API 层简化接口，`WSManager` 是底层完整实现。不宜合并。\n\n继续检查 SADP 目录状态：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_86a7688007d74248864fee6f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; if (Test-Path \"src\\ptz\\sadp\") { Get-ChildItem -Path \"src\\ptz\\sadp\" -Recurse | Select-Object FullName; echo \"---\"; Get-ChildItem -Path \"src\\ptz\" -Recurse -Directory | Select-Object FullName } else { Write-Host \"src/ptz/sadp does not exist\" }; echo \"===\"; Get-ChildItem -Path \"src\\ptz\" -Directory | Select-Object FullName","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ecf0e3af02d9421f8ca7a9bc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; Get-ChildItem -Path \"src\\ptz\" -Recurse -Directory | Select-Object FullName | Format-Table -AutoSize","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider