{"type":"message","id":"90d9405f","parentId":"48cd382a","timestamp":"2026-06-30T22:10:17.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板，AstroHub 服务返回 502 Bad Gateway。让我分析：\n\n1. 502 Bad Gateway 通常意味着反向代理（如 nginx）无法连接到后端服务\n2. 可能是：\n   - 服务还没完全启动\n   - 服务启动失败\n   - 端口冲突\n   - 配置问题\n\n根据 AGENTS.md，我**绝对不能操作网关**。但这里 AstroHub 是我开发的应用，不是 OpenClaw 网关，所以可以操作。\n\n让我检查：\n1. 服务进程是否真的启动了\n2. 检查启动日志\n3. 检查端口 10280 是否在监听\n\n我应该先检查进程状态，然后查看日志。\n\n根据 MEMORY.md，启动命令是 `python -m src.main.main --headless`，服务应该在端口 10280。\n\n让我检查：\n1. 进程是否在运行\n2. 端口是否在监听\n3. 查看日志文件\n\n这是合理的诊断步骤。\n检查服务状态：\n服务返回 502，可能启动失败。检查进程和端口：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_54b8976e625240c98e9b255d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Process python -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, ProcessName, StartTime | Format-Table -AutoSize","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2171bc52320546c7b3bc698c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"netstat -ano | findstr \":10280\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a6bcf9b1a2c241d886d646b0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; Get-Content log\\astrohub_20260701.log -Tail 30 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\n502 error means the server is not responding properly. This could be because:\n1. The server crashed during startup\n2. The server is still initializing\n3. There's an import error due to our changes\n\nLet me check the logs to see what's happening.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c3da15e7b467462393fe2c00","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; Get-Content log/astrohub_20260701.log -Tail 30 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":