{"type":"message","id":"4c2ac83a","parentId":"68d46189","timestamp":"2026-06-30T23:04:16.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tests directory is also empty or doesn't contain files. Let me understand the situation:\n\n1. AstroHub v8.01 is running successfully\n2. tests/ directory exists but is empty\n3. tools/ directory exists but is empty\n\nThe user said \"使用已有e2e测试脚本\" (use existing e2e test scripts), but I can't find any. Let me check if maybe I deleted them during the cleanup.\n\nLooking back at my cleanup list, I deleted:\n- P2: src/ptz/core/config.py, network.py, ui.py\n- P2: src/ptz/isapi/capabilities.py\n- P2: src/ascom/core/platform_detect.py\n- P2: src/core/nic_selector.py, service_manager.py\n- P2: src/database.py, env_check.py\n- P2: tests/analyze_screenshots.py\n- P2: tools/e2e_v7120_test.py\n\nWait! I deleted `tools/e2e_v7120_test.py` during the cleanup as an \"orphan file\"! This was a mistake because the user wanted to run e2e tests after the cleanup.\n\nI need to:\n1. Restore the e2e test script from backup\n2. Run the test\n\nLet me check the backup to see if the test file is there and restore it.\n我发现问题了！我在清理时删除了 `tools/e2e_v7120_test.py` 作为\"孤儿文件\"，但老板需要用它来测试！\n\n需要从备份中恢复这个测试脚本：检查备份目录中是否有 e2e_v7120_test.py 并恢复它：我发现在清理过程中我错误地删除了 `tools/e2e_v7120_test.py` 作为\"孤儿文件\"。让我检查备份目录中是否有这个文件并恢复它：发现了问题！我在清理孤儿文件时删除了 `tools/e2e_v7120_test.py`。需要从备份恢复它：","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-83c941ada6084ff19bcf982fde41c06f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"astrohub/backup_20260701_054251/tools\" -File 2>$null | Select-Object Name, Length","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":126151,"output":475,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126626,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782860633294,"res