{"type":"message","id":"9120a505","parentId":"c16bc741","timestamp":"2026-06-30T23:05:39.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我分析一下当前情况：\n\n1. 服务已在后台运行（clear-reef session）\n2. API测试结果：\n   - ✅ Devices: 200\n   - ✅ PTZ Position: 200\n   - ✅ Image Iris: 200\n   - ❌ Health: 404\n   - ❌ Version: 404\n\nHealth 和 Version 返回 404 是因为路径不对，我需要找到正确的端点。但核心的设备 API 都返回 200，说明服务正常运行。\n\n用户要求继续。我应该：\n1. 用正确的路径测试 health 和 version\n2. 总结测试结果\n3. 完成本次清理任务\n\n让我测试正确的端点。让我用正确的端点继续测试：","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## v8.01 E2E 测试（使用正确端点）\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_47f43fc3bed44ed5bd777259","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$tests = @(\n    @{Name=\"Devices\"; Url=\"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/devices\"},\n    @{Name=\"PTZ Position\"; Url=\"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\"},\n    @{Name=\"Image Iris\"; Url=\"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/iris\"},\n    @{Name=\"Image Shutter\"; Url=\"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/shutter\"},\n    @{Name=\"PTZ Capabilities\"; Url=\"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/capabilities\"}\n)\n\nforeach ($t in $tests) {\n    try {\n        $r = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $t.Url -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 5\n        Write-Host \"✅ $($t.Name): $($r.StatusCode) OK\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } catch {\n        Write-Host \"❌ $($t.Name): $($_.Exception.Message)\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    }\n}","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1193,"output":526,"cacheRead":168162,"cacheWrite":1150,"totalTokens":171031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782860723575,"responseId":"msg_391e38b9-89ba-4db5-8b2b-904ae8d7dce0"}}
