{"type":"message","id":"d3053883","parentId":"96dd14dd","timestamp":"2026-06-30T23:15:46.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error is occurring because of the triple quotes in the JavaScript string inside Python. When Python reads the file, the triple quotes `'''() => {` start a string in Python, but then there's a single quote inside which causes confusion.\n\nLet me rewrite the script to use a simpler approach - use double quotes for the Python string and single quotes inside the JavaScript. Or use a heredoc-style approach.\nJavaScript 中引号问题。修复脚本：","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The triple quotes in the JavaScript are causing issues. Let me fix the script by using a simpler approach for the JavaScript evaluation.修复 JavaScript 引号问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-5f2646b95d834c9aa8fc98cafb6443bc","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Check navigation structure\n        nav_html = await page.evaluate(\"\"\"() => {\n            const nav = document.querySelector('nav, .nav, .sidebar, .top-nav, .main-nav');\n            if (nav) return nav.innerHTML.substring(0, 2000);\n            const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('button, a, li');\n            return Array.from(buttons).slice(0, 30).map(x => x.outerHTML.substring(0, 200)).join('\\n');\n        }\"\"\")","oldText":"        # Check navigation structure\n        nav_html = await page.evaluate('''() => {\n            const nav = document.querySelector(\"nav, .nav, .sidebar, .top-nav, .main-nav\");\n            if (nav) return nav.innerHTML.substring(0, 2000);\n            \n            const buttons = document.querySelectorAll(\"button, a, li\");\n            return Array.from(buttons).slice(0, 30).map(x => x.outerHTML.substring(0, 200)).join(\"\\n\");\n        }''')"}],"path":"astrohub/tools/check_page_structure.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":136794,"output":394,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137188,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782861326284,"responseId":"cht000dd62e@dx19f1ad0ee4d2871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3ee5c95","parentId":"d3053883","timestamp":"2026-06-30T23:15:46.225Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-5f2646b95d834c9aa8fc98cafb6443bc","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in astrohub/tools/check_page_structure.py."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  8         await page.goto('http://127.0.0.1:10280')\n  9         await page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')\n 10         \n 11         # Check navigation structure\n-12         nav_html = await page.evaluate('''() => {\n-13             const nav = document.querySelector(\"nav, .nav, .sidebar, .top-nav, .main-nav\");\n+12         nav_html = await page.evaluate(\"\"\"() => {\n+13             const nav = document.querySelector('nav, .nav, .sidebar, .top-nav, .main-nav');\n 14             if (nav) return nav.innerHTML.substring(0, 2000);\n-15             \n-16             const buttons = document.querySelectorAll(\"button, a, li\");\n-17             return Array.from(buttons).slice(0, 30).map(x => x.outerHTML.substring(0, 200)).join(\"\\n\");\n-18         }''')\n+15             const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('button, a, li');\n+16             return Array.from(buttons).slice(0, 30).map(x => x.outerHTML.substring(0, 200)).join('\\n');\n+17         }\"\"\")\n 19         \n 20         print(\"=== Navigation Structure ===\")\n 21         print(nav_html[:3000])\n 22         \n    ...","firstChangedLine":12},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782861346225}}
