{"type":"message","id":"39b763c7","parentId":"25d55ff2","timestamp":"2026-06-30T23:41:37.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the situation:\n\n1. The user asked \"遇到困难了吗？设计完成了？\" (Did you encounter difficulties? Is the design complete?)\n\n2. I replied explaining the current status:\n   - API tests 6/6 passed\n   - Page loading and title check passed\n   - UI navigation tests failed due to Playwright selector syntax issues\n\n3. I tried to run the check_page_structure.py script to inspect the page structure, but got another error.\n\nThe error is in the JavaScript code passed to `page.evaluate()`. The issue is that the JavaScript code contains template literals with backticks and arrow functions, which are causing syntax errors.\n\nLooking at the error:\n```\nplaywright._impl._errors.Error: Page.evaluate: SyntaxError: Invalid or unexpected token\n```\n\nThe problem is that in Python, the triple-quoted string `\"\"\"...\"\"\"` is being interpreted, and when it's passed to JavaScript, there might be encoding issues or the JavaScript syntax is invalid.\n\nLet me check what's wrong with the JavaScript code. The code uses:\n- Template literals with backticks\n- Arrow functions\n- String concatenation\n\nThe issue might be that the Python string is not properly escaped when passed to JavaScript. I need to rewrite the check_page_structure.py script with simpler JavaScript that doesn't use template literals or complex string operations.\n\nLet me fix this by using simpler JavaScript code that avoids template literals and complex string operations.\n问题：JavaScript 代码中的模板字符串在 Python 中导致语法错误。用更简单的方式重写检查脚本：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_297332939ada4b9b8a8e7c14","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Check navigation structure\n        nav_html = await page.evaluate(\"\"\"() => {\n            var nav = document.querySelector('nav, .nav, .sidebar, .top-nav, .main-nav');\n            if (nav) return nav.innerHTML.substring(0, 2000);\n            var buttons = document.querySelectorAll('button, a, li');\n            var result = [];\n            for (var i = 0; i < Math.min(30, buttons.length); i++) {\n                result.push(buttons[i].outerHTML.substring(0, 200));\n            }\n            return result.join('\\\\n');\n        }\"\"\")","oldText":"        # Check navigation structure\n        nav_html = await page.evaluate(\"\"\"() => {\n            const nav = document.querySelector('nav, .nav, .sidebar, .top-nav, .main-nav');\n            if (nav) return nav.innerHTML.substring(0, 2000);\n            const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('button, a, li');\n            return Array.from(buttons).slice(0, 30).map(x => x.outerHTML.substring(0, 200)).join('\\n');\n        }\"\"\")"}],"path":"astrohub/tools/check_page_structure.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":3341,"output":655,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":197815,"totalTokens":201811,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782862871546,"responseId":"msg_bf5cf8d8-168a-44a2-ad1f-3d0266830174"}}
