{"type":"message","id":"46a20980","parentId":"58f14b64","timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:24:32.072Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The renderDevices function looks correct:\n- Column 1: 序号 (i+1)\n- Column 2: 设备型号 (d.model)\n- Column 3: 设备名称 (d.name || d.device_name)\n- Column 4: MAC (d.mac)\n- Column 5: IP地址 (d.ip)\n- Column 6: 网关地址 (d.gateway)\n- Column 7: 状态 (statusBadge)\n- Column 8: 操作 (actions)\n\nThis matches the table header:\n- 序号, 设备型号, 设备名称, MAC, IP地址, 网关地址, 状态, 操作\n\nThe renderDevices function seems correct. The issue might be that the `gateway` field is not being returned properly from the API response. Let me check if the API is returning the gateway field properly.\n\nActually, the user said \"网关又不能正常显示了\" - the gateway is not displaying properly again. This could mean:\n1. The gateway field is empty in the device data\n2. The API is not returning the gateway field\n3. There's a data flow issue\n\nLet me check the API endpoint that returns device data to see if it includes the gateway field. Also, let me check the POST /refresh endpoint to see if it's returning gateway properly.\n\nActually, I should check what the API returns for the devices. The issue is likely that when devices are refreshed via POST /devices/refresh, the gateway field might not be populated correctly from the SADP discovery data.\n\nLet me check the router.py to see how device data is constructed and whether gateway is included.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"列顺序和 renderDevices 函数看起来匹配。问题可能是 API 返回的设备数据中没有 `gateway` 字段。让我检查：\n\n\nAPI 端点和设备数据构造：让我检查设备刷新时网关数据是否正确传递：\n\n\n好的，让我检查 API 路由中设备状态刷新时是否正确返回 gateway 字段。\n</think>\n\n列顺序匹配：序号→型号→名称→MAC→IP→网关→状态→操作（8列）。renderDevices 也对。问题应该是 API 没返回 `gateway` 字段。检查后端数据流：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_57336e9f2fcf4877bb3bd7ae","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; Select-String -Path \"src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"gateway|get_device_by_mac|refresh\" -Context 0,3 | Select-Object -First 30","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4365,"output":558,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":188471,"totalTokens":193394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782865450506,"responseId":"msg_c672f6b4-0328-4bf0-9baa-08985a8b87b3"}}
