{"type":"message","id":"319e0e8a","parentId":"1bb08d44","timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:30:06.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到根因了！备份中的旧 ptz_controller.py 有完整的 gateway 处理逻辑（通过 ISAPI 获取设备网络信息），但在 v8.01 重构时：\n\n1. 旧的 ptz_controller.py（1800+行）被删除\n2. 新的 ptz_controller.py 被瘦身，移除了 ISAPI 相关代码\n3. 网关获取逻辑（通过 `/ISAPI/System/network/interfaces` 或 `/ISAPI/Network/channels/1/Network`）也被移除了\n\n现在 SADP 回调虽然设置了 gateway 字段（第819行），但如果设备不广播网关（常见情况），gateway 就为空。\n\n解决方案：设备连接时通过 ISAPI 获取网络配置并存储网关。\n\n让我检查当前代码中是否有获取网络配置的逻辑：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7e6fb78e48b249f281b00daa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; Select-String -Path \"src\\**\\*.py\" -Pattern \"network|Network|gateway\" | Select-Object -First 30","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":8431,"output":263,"cacheRead":117188,"cacheWrite":17096,"totalTokens":142978,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782865783441,"responseId":"msg_ca8fb2ad-508b-4652-b6d8-e4b636b337d8"}}
