{"type":"message","id":"b15fe04e","parentId":"40f48583","timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:36:48.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to write lasting notes to memory/2026-07-01.md. Let me think about what's worth storing from this session:\n\n1. v8.01 cleanup was completed - already documented\n2. E2E tests were run - already documented in HEARTBEAT.md\n3. Gateway display bug was identified - this is important to track\n\nThe gateway issue is a bug that needs to be tracked. I should add this to the memory file so it's not forgotten.\n\nLet me check what's already in memory/2026-07-01.md and append only new information.\n\nFrom the context, I know:\n- v8.01 was released\n- E2E tests ran with 73% pass rate\n- Gateway display issue was discovered and diagnosed\n- A fix proposal was submitted\n\nThis should be appended to the memory file.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2a4340b7e7974f8c86306c9e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-07-01.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2428,"output":233,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":83667,"totalTokens":86328,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782866198866,"responseId":"msg_11e879b7-c98b-4327-a647-c2be8695867c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a3c71c2","parentId":"b15fe04e","timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:36:48.971Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_2a4340b7e7974f8c86306c9e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-07-01\n\n## v8.01 代码清理重构（主要工作）\n\n### 完成的任务\n1. **Logger 重命名**\n   - `src/ptz/core/logger.py`: `Logger` → `PTZLogger`（避免与全局 Logger 混淆）\n   - 修复 `Logger.silent` → `PTZLogger.silent`\n\n2. **ptz_controller.py 瘦身**\n   - 删除内嵌 `Logger` 类（约 10KB）\n   - 删除内嵌 `ISAPIResponse` + `ISAPIClient`（约 10KB）\n   - 总计减少约 20KB 重复代码\n   - 复用独立模块：`src/ptz/core/logger.py` 和 `src/ptz/isapi/client.py`\n\n3. **Orchestrator 重命名**\n   - `src/core/orchestrator.py`: `Orchestrator` → `TaskScheduler`\n   - 更新所有引用（router.py, core/__init__.py, main.py）\n\n4. **版本更新**\n   - `src/main/constants.py`: VERSION = \"8.01\", VERSION_NUM = \"8.01\"\n\n5. **其他清理**\n   - 删除未使用的 `src/ptz/sadp/` 目录\n   - 清理冗余配置文件\n   - 优化依赖关系\n\n### 文件修改统计\n- 修改: 15 个文件\n- 删除: 8 个文件\n- 新增: 2 个文件（E2E 测试脚本）\n\n### E2E 测试结果\n- **总体**: 22 项测试 | 通过 16 | 失败 6 | 通过率 73%\n- **API 测试**: 6/6 全部通过 (100%)\n- **核心功能**: Function/Speed/Limit 全部执行成功\n- **UI 定位问题**: 6 项失败（主要是选择器匹配问题，不影响功能）\n\n### 测试产物\n- E2E 脚本: `astrohub/tools/e2e_v801_simple.py`\n- 截图: `astrohub/e2e_screenshots/`\n- 结果: `astrohub/e2e_screenshots/results.json`\n\n### 验证结论\n- ✅ API 层全部正常\n- ✅ 核心功能验证成功\n- ✅ 服务运行稳定\n- ⚠️ UI 定位问题可在后续迭代中优化\n\n---\n\n## v7.122 前端修复（上午完成）\n\n### 三个修复\n1. **连接成功提示缺失** — `connectDevice()` 主路径缺少 `showToast('success')`\n2. **切换设备页面不刷新状态** — `loadDevicesQuick()` 竞态覆盖 `refreshDevices()`\n3. **列顺序调整** — 序号|设备型号|设备名称|MAC|IP|网关|状态|操作\n\n### 涉及文件\n- `src/web/index.html` — 三处修改\n- `src/web/includes/devices.html` — 表头列顺序\n- `src/main/constants.py` — 版本号 v7.122\n\n### 备份\n- `backup_20260701_043220/`\n- `D:\\astrohub_backup_20260701` (Git 已推送)\n\n### E2E 验证\n- 截图确认列顺序正确 ✅\n- 截图确认状态显示\"已连接\" ✅\n- API 确认 refresh 返回 status: \"已连接\" ✅\n\n---\n\n## 复盘教训\n\n### 1. 多入口UI操作只改一处\n- `switchPage()` 和 `initNav` click handler 是两个独立入口\n- 只改了 switchPage，漏了 initNav → 状态仍显示离线\n- **教训**：修改UI行为 → 搜索所有触发路径 → 逐一确认\n\n### 2. 异步竞态覆盖\n- `loadDevicesQuick()`(GET,无status) 和 `refreshDevices()`(POST,有status) 同时触发\n- 无status的GET后返回，覆盖了有status的POST结果\n- **教训**：两个async写同一个UI → 合并为一个请求，或用标志位阻止覆盖\n\n### 3. 多分支函数遗漏分支\n- `connectDevice()` 有3个成功路径，主路径缺 `showToast`\n- 只检查了路径2/3认为\"已有\"，漏了路径1\n- **教训**：列出所有 if/else/catch 分支 → 逐一检查用户反馈\n\n### 4. E2E 测试选择器优化\n- Playwright 的 `text=\"xxx\"` 选择器在复杂 UI 中容易超时\n- **建议**: 优先使用更稳定的选择器（如 `data-testid`、role、name）\n- **教训**: UI 自动化测试需要稳定的元素定位策略\n\n---\n\n## 备份规范\n- D盘备份路径: `D:\\astrohub_backup_YYYYMMDD`\n- Git 仓库: https://github.com/hackersb46-glitch/astrohub\n- 备份后需 Git push\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782866208971}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a66b76f","parentId":"0a3c71c2","timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:37:12.831Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked me to write any lasting notes to memory/2026-07-01.md. Let me think about what's worth storing:\n\n1. The gateway display issue was discovered after v8.01 refactoring\n2. Root cause: ISAPI network config fetching logic was removed during ptz_controller.py slimming\n3. This is an important regression that needs to be tracked\n\nThe memory file already has the v8.01 refactoring work documented. I should add:\n- The gateway bug discovery and diagnosis\n- The proposed fix approach\n- This is a critical regression to track\n\nI should append this information to the existing memory file.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_69f831d79db242f19af33273","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\n---\n\n## 🔴 网关显示问题（v8.01 回归 Bug）\n\n### 发现时间\n2026-07-01 08:33\n\n### 现象\n设备管理页面「网关地址」列为空，API 返回 `\"gateway\": \"\"`\n\n### 根因\n**v8.01 重构时丢失了 ISAPI 网络配置获取逻辑**\n\n| 位置 | 旧代码（已删除） | 状态 |\n|------|-----------------|------|\n| `backup_*/src/core/ptz_controller.py:443-445` | 从 ISAPI 响应解析 `IPv4Gateway` | ❌ 已删除 |\n| `backup_*/src/core/ptz_controller.py:1369` | `client.get_xml_text(root, \"defaultGateway\", \"\")` | ❌ 已删除 |\n| `src/ptz/isapi/client.py` | 无网络配置获取方法 | ❌ 缺失 |\n\n**SADP 回调**（`src/ptz/sadp/discovery.py` 第819行）虽然会解析 `szIPv4Gateway`，但设备通常不通过 SADP 广播网关地址。\n\n### 修复方案（待审核）\n\n**在 `src/ptz/isapi/client.py` 中添加 `get_network_info()` 方法：**\n\n```python\ndef get_network_info(self) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"获取设备网络配置（IP/子网/网关）。\n    \n    尝试端点: /System/network/interfaces 或 /Network/channels/1\n    \n    Returns:\n        {\"ip\": ..., \"subnet_mask\": ..., \"gateway\": ...} 或 {}\n    \"\"\"\n    endpoints = [\"/System/network/interfaces\", \"/Network/channels/1\"]\n    for ep in endpoints:\n        resp = self.get(ep)\n        if resp.status_code == 200 and resp.xml:\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            return {\n                \"ip\": self.get_xml_text(root, \"ipAddress\", \"\"),\n                \"subnet_mask\": self.get_xml_text(root, \"subnetMask\", \"\"),\n                \"gateway\": self.get_xml_text(root, \"defaultGateway\", \"\"),\n            }\n    return {}\n```\n\n**在设备连接成功时调用并存储：**\n\n位置：`src/api/router.py` 的 `connect_device()` 成功分支中\n\n```python\n# 连接成功后获取网络配置\nnet_info = client.get_network_info()\nif net_info.get(\"gateway\"):\n    # 存储到设备 info.json\n    config.upsert_device(mac, {\"gateway\": net_info[\"gateway\"], ...})\n```\n\n### 影响范围\n- `src/ptz/isapi/client.py` — 新增 1 个方法（~25行）\n- `src/api/router.py` — 连接成功时调用（~5行）\n- 无破坏性变更，纯增量修复\n\n### 状态\n⏳ **待老板审核后修复**\n\n### 教训\n- 重构时删除代码前，必须检查该代码的唯一功能是否在其他地方有替代\n- 特别是「获取并存储」逻辑，删除后会导致数据缺失\n- E2E 测试应包含数据完整性验证（不仅检查 API 返回 200，还要检查字段非空）\n","path":"memory/2026-07-01.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2506,"output":919,"cacheRead":83667,"cacheWrite":1312,"totalTokens":88404,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782866208973,"responseId":"msg_2aba8d68-8c16-41fe-90dc-5761c9237d8f"}}
