{"type":"message","id":"58b97107","parentId":"f3b9cf4f","timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:38:47.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说nano-pdf技能不存在。让我检查一下可用的技能列表，看看是否有其他方式读取PDF。\n\n让我检查有哪些技能可用。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2ac051f213c44c02ae1a60f7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\skills\" -Filter \"SKILL.md\" -Recurse | Select-Object FullName","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n</think>\n\n用户要我读取 HIKVISION ISAPI 2.0 PDF 文档，找出正确的网络配置端点。PDF 有 285 页，在 `D:\\SDK\\HIK SDK\\isapi_temp\\HIKVISION ISAPI_2.0-IPMD Service.pdf`。\n\n我需要用 Python 的 PyPDF2 或类似库来读取 PDF 内容。让我直接搜索文档中的关键词，比如 \"network\"、\"gateway\"、\"Network\" 等。\n\n让我先安装必要的库（如果需要），然后提取 PDF 内容。好，让我用 Python 直接读取 PDF 内容，搜索网络配置相关的端点：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_fed5593a0da7483084c922d0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport PyPDF2\n\nwith open('ISAPI_doc.pdf', 'rb') as f:\n    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)\n    \n    # 搜索包含 'network' 或 'gateway' 的页面\n    keywords = ['gateway', 'network', 'Network', 'Gateway']\n    found_pages = []\n    \n    for i, page in enumerate(reader.pages):\n        text = page.extract_text()\n        for keyword in keywords:\n            if keyword.lower() in text.lower():\n                found_pages.append(i + 1)\n                break\n    \n    print(f'Found {len(found_pages)} pages with network/gateway keywords')\n    print(f'Pages: {found_pages[:20]}')  # 显示前20个\n\"","timeout":60,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1070,"output":493,"cacheRead":256531,"cacheWrite":278,"totalTokens":258372,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782866311338,"responseId":"msg_831e0ec0-4e54-4bb9-956e-06ccb61b9a7b"}}
