{"type":"message","id":"aa66c65f","parentId":"03ae06d3","timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:39:42.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The PDF extraction failed due to encoding issues. Let me try a different approach - write to a file instead of printing directly.\n\nActually, let me try to directly use curl to test the ISAPI endpoint on the device to see what the actual response looks like. Since the device is connected (192.168.5.72), I can test the actual ISAPI endpoint.\n\nLet me try to call the ISAPI endpoint directly to see the XML structure.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我直接测试设备的实际 ISAPI 端点，获取真实的 XML 响应结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-cd230fff5ae0471aa147ae08bebb2efb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\n\n# 测试设备的 ISAPI 网络接口端点\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\n\n# 尝试多个可能的端点\nendpoints = [\n    '/ISAPI/System/Network/interfaces',\n    '/ISAPI/System/network/interfaces',\n    '/ISAPI/System/Network/interfaces/1',\n    '/ISAPI/System/network/interfaces/1',\n]\n\nfor ep in endpoints:\n    url = f'http://{ip}{ep}'\n    try:\n        r = requests.get(url, auth=auth, timeout=5)\n        print(f'{ep}: status={r.status_code}')\n        if r.status_code == 200:\n            print(r.text[:500])\n            print('---')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{ep}: error={e}')\n\"","timeout":30,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":140729,"output":341,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141070,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782866368427,"responseId":"cht000d1c68@dx19f1b1de12929c2503"}}
