{"type":"message","id":"061b82cb","parentId":"0fa9c68f","timestamp":"2026-07-01T01:22:25.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I have a list of all Python files in astrohub. I need to:\n1. Record the gateway finding to memory/2026-07-01.md\n2. Classify each file by SDK type:\n   - SADP-related files\n   - ISAPI-related files\n   - WASM/streaming files\n   - Other SDKs or independent files\n3. Identify cross-references and dependencies\n\nLet me scan for SADP, ISAPI, WASM references across the codebase.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好，我来：\n1. 先记录发现到 memory/2026-07-01.md\n2. 遍历代码，按 SDK 分类\n3. 找出其他 SDK\n4. 制定重构计划"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-72ab3b35f531463ca1722cf9fe05fe47","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"\n### 待修复：网关字段丢失\n\n**根因**：SADP SDK 已具备获取网关能力，`sadp_discovery.py:819` 正确解析 `szIPv4Gateway`，但 `Device` 模型和 `_save()` 方法未定义/保存 `gateway` 字段。\n\n**数据流断裂点**：\n```\nSADP SDK → szIPv4Gateway[16] ✅\n  ↓\nsadp_discovery.py:819 → device.gateway ✅\n  ↓\nDevice 类 → ❌ 没有 gateway 字段\n  ↓\n_save() → ❌ 没有保存 gateway\n  ↓\ninfo.json → ❌ 没有 gateway\n```\n\n**修复点**：`src/core/device_manager.py`\n- Device 类添加 `gateway: str = \"\"` 和 `subnet_mask: str = \"\"`\n- `_save()` 中增加 gateway、subnet_mask 到 dev_data\n- `_load()` 中恢复 gateway\n\n---\n\n## v8.02 重构计划（待执行）\n\n### 目标\n按 SDK 分类整合脚本：SADP 类统一命名，ISAPI 类统一命名，WASM 保持不变。\n\n### 脚本分类现状（待遍历确认）\n\n| 分类 | 现状脚本 | 功能 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **SADP** | `src/core/sadp_discovery.py` | 设备发现、修改 IP（DLL） |\n| **ISAPI** | `src/ptz/isapi/client.py` | HTTP 客户端（GET/PUT/XML） |\n| **ISAPI** | `src/ptz/isapi/ptz.py` | PTZ 控制（运动/预设/能力） |\n| **ISAPI** | `src/core/ptz_controller.py` | 设备控制器（整合 ISAPI） |\n| **WASM** | `src/stream_in/core/proxy.py` | WebSocket 代理 |\n| **WASM** | 前端 `index.html` | WASM 播放器 |\n","oldText":"\n### 待修复：网关字段丢失（待 v8.02）\n\n**根因**：SADP SDK 具备获取网关能力，但 Device 模型和 _save() 未保存 gateway 字段。\n\n**修复点**：\n- Device 类添加 `gateway: str = \"\"` 和 `subnet_mask: str = \"\"`\n- `_save()` 中增加 gateway、subnet_mask 到 dev_data\n- `_load()` 中恢复 gateway\n"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\memory\\2026-07-01.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":57016,"output":777,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782868906354,"responseId":"cht000d4229@dx19f1b44a3dc29c2503"}}
