{"type":"message","id":"7515f76a","parentId":"0f11ad66","timestamp":"2026-07-01T03:51:20.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户纠正我了 - 他说的是\"先修复脚本，再重新测试\"。我理解错了顺序。我应该：\n\n1. 先修复 e2e_v801_full.py 中的 CSS 选择器问题\n2. 然后再运行测试\n\n让我立即修复测试脚本中的 CSS 选择器语法错误。\n\n问题是 `button:has-text(\"xxx\")` 不是有效的 CSS 选择器。Playwright 的正确语法应该是：\n- `button >> text=\"控制台\"` \n- 或者使用 Playwright 的文本选择器: `:text(\"控制台\")`\n- 或者直接用 `button:has(:text(\"控制台\"))`\n\n\n- 最简单的办法是直接用文本选择器 `text=\"控制台\"` 或者用 `data-page` 属性选择器来定位元素，这样更直接有效。\n\n现在我要查看测试脚本里具体用了哪些选择器，然后根据这个思路来修复。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我的错。立即修复测试脚本。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cbae499d51964060835f2494","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content astrohub/tools/e2e_v801_full.py | Select-String -Pattern \"has-text|data-page|text=\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":210,"output":267,"cacheRead":111234,"cacheWrite":2083,"totalTokens":113794,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782877854441,"responseId":"msg_b911618c-5995-4145-9796-0cead2a745e8"}}
