{"type":"message","id":"466e54a5","parentId":"6bfc5395","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:07:15.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is telling me that I failed the edit and that I need to check the structure first. They said \"主控台\" not \"控制台\".\n\nLooking at the page structure I just retrieved:\n```\n<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"console\">主控台</button>\n```\n\nSo it's \"主控台\" (main console), not \"控制台\" (control console).\n\nThe navigation buttons use `data-page` attribute, and the structure is:\n- `data-page=\"dashboard\"` - 仪表盘\n- `data-page=\"devices\"` - 设备管理\n- `data-page=\"console\"` - 主控台\n- `data-page=\"observation\"` - 观测计划\n- `data-page=\"advanced\"` - 高级功能\n- `data-page=\"replay\"` - 回放\n- `data-page=\"settings\"` - 设置\n\nThe user said \"你应该先搞清楚结构再写脚本\" - meaning I should understand the structure first before writing the script.\n\nI need to:\n1. Read the full HTML structure\n2. Understand the navigation and elements\n3. Then fix the test script properly\n\nLet me read the actual HTML file first.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我错了。先搞清楚结构。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_13888ca50e0748ea8659c9e4","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"path":"astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":947,"output":302,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":115916,"totalTokens":117165,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782878818172,"responseId":"msg_391b9546-dad0-49bf-bbe4-3671a9011a31"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c153a9df","parentId":"466e54a5","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:07:15.788Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_13888ca50e0748ea8659c9e4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>AstroHub</title>\r\n    <!-- JSPlugin URL 解析不支持 localhost,必须用 IP -->\r\n    <script>\r\n    (function(){\r\n        if (location.hostname === 'localhost') {\r\n            var port = location.port || (location.protocol === 'https:' ? '443' : '80');\r\n            var newHost = '127.0.0.1';\r\n            // 尝试获取本机 IP,失败则用 127.0.0.1\r\n            var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();\r\n            xhr.open('GET', '/api/v1/localhost', false); // 同步请求\r\n            try {\r\n                xhr.send();\r\n                if (xhr.status === 200) {\r\n                    var data = JSON.parse(xhr.responseText);\r\n                    if (data.success && data.data && data.data.local_ip) {\r\n                        newHost = data.data.local_ip;\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            } catch(e) {}\r\n            location.replace(location.protocol + '//' + newHost + ':' + port + location.pathname + location.search + location.hash);\r\n        }\r\n    })();\r\n    </script>\r\n    <!-- WASM SDK: 严格复用官方 WebSDK_noPlugin 方式 -->\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/jsPlugin/jquery.min.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/encryption/crypto-3.1.2.min.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/encryption/cryptico.min.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/webVideoCtrl.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/js/wasm-player.js\"></script>\r\n    <style>\r\n        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }\r\n        body { font-family: -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background:#0a0e17; color:#e0e6f0; min-height:100vh; }\r\n        .header { background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1e2e, #0d1117); padding:12px 24px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; }\r\n        .logo { font-size:24px; font-weight:700; color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .logo span { color:#f0883e; }\r\n        .version { font-size:12px; color:#8b949e; background:#21262d; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:12px; }\r\n        .status-bar { display:flex; gap:16px; align-items:center; }\r\n        .status-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; font-size:13px; }\r\n        .status-dot { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; }\r\n        .status-dot.green { background:#3fb950; box-shadow:0 0 6px #3fb950; }\r\n        .status-dot.yellow { background:#d29922; box-shadow:0 0 6px #d29922; }\r\n        .status-dot.red { background:#f85149; box-shadow:0 0 6px #f85149; }\r\n        .status-dot.blue { background:#58a6ff; box-shadow:0 0 6px #58a6ff; }\r\n        /* 开关样式 */\r\n        .switch { position:relative; display:inline-block; width:36px; height:18px; }\r\n        .switch input { opacity:0; width:0; height:0; }\r\n        .slider { position:absolute; cursor:pointer; top:0; left:0; right:0; bottom:0; background-color:#30363d; transition:.2s; border-radius:18px; }\r\n        .slider:before { position:absolute; content:\"\"; height:12px; width:12px; left:3px; bottom:3px; background-color:#8b949e; transition:.2s; border-radius:50%; }\r\n        input:checked + .slider { background-color:#238636; }\r\n        input:checked + .slider:before { transform:translateX(18px); background-color:#fff; }\r\n        .nav { background:#161b22; padding:8px 24px; display:flex; gap:4px; align-items:center; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        .nav-btn { background:none; border:none; color:#8b949e; padding:8px 16px; cursor:pointer; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; transition:all 0.2s; }\r\n        .nav-btn:hover { background:#21262d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .nav-btn.active { background:#238636; color:#fff; }\r\n        /* --- Advanced Page: Left Sidebar Layout --- */\r\n        .advanced-layout { display:flex; gap:0; min-height:600px; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar { width:200px; background:#161b22; border-right:1px solid #21262d; padding:8px 0; flex-shrink:0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item { background:none; border:none; color:#8b949e; padding:10px 16px; cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; transition:all 0.2s; width:100%; text-align:left; display:block; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item:hover { background:#21262d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item.active { background:#238636; color:#fff; border-left:3px solid #3fb950; }\r\n        .advanced-content { flex:1; min-width:0; padding:20px; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page { display:none; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page.active { display:block; }\r\n        /* --- Observation Page Layout --- */\r\n        .observation-layout { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:20px; }\r\n        .obs-card { background:#161b22; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; }\r\n        .obs-card h3 { font-size:15px; color:#58a6ff; margin-bottom:12px; padding-bottom:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; }\r\n        .obs-placeholder { color:#6e7681; font-size:13px; padding:20px 0; text-align:center; }\r\n        .obs-actions { margin-top:16px; display:flex; gap:8px; justify-content:flex-end; }\r\n        .main { padding:20px 24px; }\r\n        .page { display:none; }\r\n        .page.active { display:block; }\r\n        .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap:16px; margin-bottom:20px; }\r\n        .card { background:#161b22; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; transition:border-color 0.2s; }\r\n        .card:hover { border-color:#30363d; }\r\n        .card-title { font-size:12px; color:#8b949e; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:8px; }\r\n        .card-value { font-size:32px; font-weight:700; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .card-value.green { color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .card-sub { font-size:12px; color:#6e7681; margin-top:4px; }\r\n        table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; }\r\n        th, td { text-align:left; padding:10px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; font-size:14px; }\r\n        th { color:#8b949e; font-weight:500; background:#0d1117; }\r\n        tr:hover { background:#161b22; }\r\n        .badge { padding:2px 8px; border-radius:12px; font-size:12px; font-weight:500; }\r\n        .badge.online { background:rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .badge.offline { background:rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color:#f85149; }\r\n        .badge.yes { background:rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .badge.no { background:rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color:#f85149; }\r\n        .ptz-controls { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 48px); gap:5px; justify-content:center; margin:6px 0; }\r\n        .ptz-btn { width:48px; height:48px; border:1px solid #30363d; border-radius:8px; background:#161b22; color:#e0e6f0; font-size:17px; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; transition:all 0.15s; }\r\n        .ptz-btn:hover { background:#238636; border-color:#238636; }\r\n        .ptz-btn.center { background:#21262d; cursor:default; }\r\n        .ptz-btn.center:hover { background:#21262d; transform:none; }\r\n        .ptz-btn:active:not(.center) { transform:scale(0.95); }\r\n        .ptz-speed { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; justify-content:center; margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .ptz-speed input[type=range] { width:200px; accent-color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .form-group { margin-bottom:16px; }\r\n        .form-group label { display:block; font-size:14px; color:#8b949e; margin-bottom:6px; }\r\n        .form-group input, .form-group select { width:100%; padding:10px 12px; background:#0d1117; border:1px solid #30363d; border-radius:6px; color:#e0e6f0; font-size:14px; }\r\n        .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus { outline:none; border-color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .btn { padding:10px 20px; border:none; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; }\r\n        .btn-primary { background:#238636; color:#fff; }\r\n        .btn-primary:hover { background:#2ea043; }\r\n        .btn-secondary { background:#30363d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .btn-secondary:hover { background:#484f58; }\r\n        .btn-danger { background:#da3633; color:#fff; }\r\n        .btn-danger:hover { background:#f85149; }\r\n        .btn-warning { background:#d29922; color:#0d1117; }\r\n        .btn-warning:hover { background:#e3b341; }\r\n        .btn-sm { padding:6px 12px; font-size:12px; }\r\n        .btn:disabled { opacity:0.5; cursor:not-allowed; }\r\n        .btn-group { display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        .progress-bar { height:8px; background:#21262d; border-radius:4px; overflow:hidden; }\r\n        .progress-fill { height:100%; border-radius:4px; transition:width 0.3s; }\r\n        .progress-fill.green { background:#3fb950; }\r\n        .progress-fill.yellow { background:#d29922; }\r\n        .progress-fill.red { background:#f85149; }\r\n        .progress-fill.blue { background:#58a6ff; }\r\n        /* Advanced page status panel */\r\n        .advanced-status-panel { background:#0d1117; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .advanced-status-panel h4 { font-size:15px; color:#e0e6f0; margin-bottom:12px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; padding-bottom:8px; }\r\n        .status-row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:6px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; font-size:14px; }\r\n        .status-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }\r\n        .status-label { color:#8b949e; }\r\n        .status-value { color:#e0e6f0; font-family:monospace; }\r\n        .adv-header { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        .adv-header select { max-width:300px; }\r\n        .result-table { margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .progress-section { margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .progress-text { font-size:13px; color:#8b949e; margin-bottom:4px; }\r\n        .current-direction { font-size:18px; color:#58a6ff; font-family:monospace; text-align:center; padding:8px; background:#0d1117; border-radius:8px; margin:12px 0; }\r\n        .log-entry { padding:6px 12px; border-left:3px solid #30363d; margin-bottom:4px; font-size:13px; font-family:monospace; }\r\n        .log-entry.info { border-color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .log-entry.warn { border-color:#d29922; }\r\n        .log-entry.error { border-color:#f85149; }\r\n        .log-entry.success { border-color:#3fb950; }\r\n        /* Toast notification */\r\n        .toast-container { position:fixed; top:60px; right:24px; z-index:9999; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }\r\n        .toast { padding:12px 20px; border-radius:8px; font-size:14px; animation:slideIn 0.3s ease; min-width:250px; max-width:400px; }\r\n        .toast.success { background:#1a4731; border:1px solid #3fb950; color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .toast.error { background:#4d1c1a; border:1px solid #f85149; color:#f85149; }\r\n        .toast.info { background:#1a3a52; border:1px solid #58a6ff; color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .toast.warning { background:#4a3a1a; border:1px solid #d29922; color:#d29922; }\r\n        @keyframes slideIn { from { transform:translateX(100%); opacity:0; } to { transform:translateX(0); opacity:1; } }\r\n        /* Unified Modal (v7.117) */\r\n        .astro-modal-backdrop { position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.65); z-index:10000; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }\r\n        .astro-modal { background:#1a1e2e; border:1px solid #30363d; border-radius:12px; padding:24px; min-width:320px; max-width:480px; box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); }\r\n        .astro-modal-title { margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; font-weight:600; }\r\n        .astro-modal-body { margin:0 0 20px 0; color:#e0e6f0; line-height:1.6; font-size:14px; }\r\n        .astro-modal-actions { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:flex-end; }\r\n        .astro-modal-field { margin-bottom:14px; }\r\n        .astro-modal-field label { display:block; margin-bottom:6px; color:#8b949e; font-size:13px; }\r\n        .astro-modal-field input { width:100%; padding:10px; background:#0d1117; border:1px solid #30363d; border-radius:6px; color:#e0e6f0; font-size:14px; box-sizing:border-box; }\r\n        .astro-modal-field input:focus { outline:none; border-color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        /* Loading spinner */\r\n        .spinner { display:inline-block; width:16px; height:16px; border:2px solid #30363d; border-top-color:#58a6ff; border-radius:50%; animation:spin 0.8s linear infinite; }\r\n        @keyframes spin { to { transform:rotate(360deg); } }\r\n        .loading { pointer-events:none; opacity:0.7; }\r\n        /* Device actions */\r\n        .actions { display:flex; gap:4px; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        /* PTZ status panel */\r\n        .ptz-position { text-align:center; padding:12px; background:#0d1117; border-radius:8px; margin:12px 0; font-family:monospace; font-size:14px; }\r\n        .toolbar { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:16px; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        .toolbar-actions { display:flex; gap:8px; }\r\n        .device-info-panel { background:#0d1117; border-radius:8px; padding:16px; margin-top:12px; font-size:13px; }\r\n        .device-info-panel .info-row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:4px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; }\r\n        .device-info-panel .info-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }\r\n        .device-info-panel .info-label { color:#8b949e; }\r\n        .device-info-panel .info-value { color:#e0e6f0; font-family:monospace; }\r\n        @media (max-width:768px) { .grid { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; } .header { flex-direction:column; gap:8px; } .nav { overflow-x:auto; } .console-layout { flex-direction:column !important; } .console-left, .console-center, .console-right { width:100% !important; } }\r\n        /* Console page: left-right layout (SPEC: left=joystick, right=display) */\r\n        .console-layout { display:flex; gap:20px; align-items:flex-start; }\r\n        .console-left { flex:0 0 320px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; min-width:0; overflow:hidden; }\r\n        .console-center { flex:1; min-width:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }\r\n        .console-right { flex:0 0 25%; max-width:300px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }\r\n        /* WASM 播放器容器: 强制子元素填满, 保持 16:9 */\r\n        #divPlugin { width:100%; aspect-ratio:16/9; display:block; overflow:hidden; }\r\n        #divPlugin .parent-wnd { width:100% !important; height:100% !important; }\r\n        #divPlugin .parent-wnd > div { width:100% !important; height:100% !important; border:none !important; }\r\n        #divPlugin .video-container { width:100% !important; height:100% !important; }\r\n        #divPlugin canvas.play-window { width:100% !important; height:100% !important; }\r\n        /* 隐藏滚动条(鼠标滚轮仍可滚动) */\r\n        .hide-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }\r\n        .hide-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <div class=\"header\">\r\n        <div class=\"logo\">Astro<span>Hub</span></div>\r\n        <div class=\"status-bar\">\r\n            <div class=\"status-item\"><span class=\"status-dot red\" id=\"wsDot\"></span><span id=\"wsStatus\">ISAPI: 未连接</span></div>\r\n            <div class=\"status-item\"><span class=\"status-dot red\" id=\"mediaInputDot\"></span><span id=\"mediaInputStatus\">媒体输入: 等待连接</span></div>\r\n            <div class=\"status-item\"><span class=\"status-dot\" id=\"mediaOutputDot\" style=\"background:#30363d;box-shadow:none\"></span><span id=\"mediaOutputStatus\">未录制</span></div>\r\n            <div class=\"status-item\" id=\"clock\"></div>\r\n            <!-- 快速连接开关 -->\r\n\n[2675 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782878835788}}
{"type":"message","id":"be635e03","parentId":"c153a9df","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:07:36.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I see the navigation structure from lines 201-300. Let me find the actual nav buttons with their text. I can see from the curl output earlier that the buttons are:\n- `data-page=\"dashboard\"` - 仪表盘\n- `data-page=\"devices\"` - 设备管理\n- `data-page=\"console\"` - 主控台\n- `data-page=\"observation\"` - 观测计划\n- `data-page=\"advanced\"` - 高级功能\n- `data-page=\"replay\"` - 回放\n- `data-page=\"settings\"` - 设置\n\nI need to look at the actual HTML to see the exact button text. Let me continue reading the file to find the nav section.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d9c709f01c0541ff861bfd43","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":201,"path":"astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":5567,"output":213,"cacheRead":115916,"cacheWrite":941,"totalTokens":122637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782878835790,"responseId":"msg_27b919d4-19c3-4136-a2be-3671a72d8fd3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8460787","parentId":"be635e03","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:07:36.622Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_d9c709f01c0541ff861bfd43","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            <div class=\"status-item\">\r\n                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px\">快速连接</span>\r\n                <label class=\"switch\">\r\n                    <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"quickConnectSwitch\" onchange=\"quickConnect(this.checked)\">\r\n                    <span class=\"slider\"></span>\r\n                </label>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <!-- 重启按钮 -->\r\n            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"confirmRestart()\" style=\"padding:2px 8px\">重启</button>\r\n            <span class=\"version\" id=\"version-display\">...</span>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"nav\">\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn active\" data-page=\"dashboard\">仪表盘</button>\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"devices\">设备管理</button>\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"console\">主控台</button>\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"observation\">观测计划</button>\r\n        <!-- Advanced Features: 校准 功能测试 限位测试 速度测试 推流/存储 -->\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"advanced\">高级功能</button>\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"replay\">回放</button>\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"settings\">设置</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"main\">\r\n        <!-- ==================== 仪表盘 ==================== -->\r\n\r\n        <!-- ==================== Page Modules ==================== -->\r\n        {% include \"includes/dashboard.html\" %}\r\n        {% include \"includes/devices.html\" %}\r\n        {% include \"includes/console.html\" %}\r\n        {% include \"includes/observation.html\" %}\r\n        {% include \"includes/advanced.html\" %}\r\n        {% include \"includes/replay.html\" %}\r\n        <!-- ==================== 设置 ==================== -->\r\n        <div class=\"page\" id=\"page-settings\">\r\n            <div style=\"max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px\">\r\n                <h2 style=\"color:#e0e6f0;margin-bottom:20px\"></h2>\r\n                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap\">\r\n                    <!-- 存储路径 -->\r\n                    <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:380px\">\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"storageSettingsSection\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('storageSettingsSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">💾 存储路径</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px\">\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <label style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px;display:block;margin-bottom:4px\">录制存储路径(截图+录像统一)</label>\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"settingRecordPath\" style=\"flex:1;padding:8px 12px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px\" placeholder=\"data/records\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"selectFolder('settingRecordPath')\">浏览</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div style=\"margin-top:8px\">\r\n                                        <span id=\"settingsSaveStatus\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#3fb950\"></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <!-- 配置路径 -->\r\n                    <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:380px\">\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"configPathSection\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('configPathSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">📁 配置路径</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px\">\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <label style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px;display:block;margin-bottom:4px\">本机配置</label>\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"settingLocalConfig\" style=\"flex:1;padding:8px 12px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px\" readonly>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"selectFolder('settingLocalConfig')\">浏览</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <label style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px;display:block;margin-bottom:4px\">设备配置</label>\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"settingDeviceConfig\" style=\"flex:1;padding:8px 12px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px\" readonly>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"selectFolder('settingDeviceConfig')\">浏览</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <label style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px;display:block;margin-bottom:4px\">测试数据</label>\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"settingTestData\" style=\"flex:1;padding:8px 12px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px\" readonly>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"selectFolder('settingTestData')\">浏览</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div style=\"margin-top:8px\">\r\n                                        <span id=\"configSaveStatus\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#3fb950\"></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <!-- 扩展路径 -->\r\n                <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"extPathSection\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px\">\r\n\n[2575 more lines in file. Use offset=301 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782878856622}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c506676","parentId":"a8460787","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:08:12.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我修复测试脚本，但我之前没有仔细阅读页面结构就尝试修复。现在我已经看到了 index.html 的实际内容，我需要：\n\n1. 先理解页面结构\n2. 然后查看测试脚本\n3. 根据实际结构修复脚本\n\n从 index.html 第 218-228 行，我可以看到导航按钮的结构：\n```html\n<div class=\"nav\">\n    <button class=\"nav-btn active\" data-page=\"dashboard\">仪表盘</button>\n    <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"devices\">设备管理</button>\n    <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"console\">主控台</button>\n    <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"observation\">观测计划</button>\n    <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"advanced\">高级功能</button>\n    <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"replay\">回放</button>\n    <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"settings\">设置</button>\n</div>\n```\n\n关键信息：\n- 导航按钮有 `data-page` 属性\n- 按钮文本是中文：仪表盘、设备管理、主控台、观测计划、高级功能、回放、设置\n- 之前测试脚本用的是 `has-text(\"控制台\")`，但实际应该是 `主控台`\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 读取测试脚本 e2e_v801_full.py\n2. 理解它要测试什么\n3. 根据实际页面结构修复选择器\n\n让我先读取测试脚本。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在我已经看到了页面结构。导航按钮在第218-228行，使用 `data-page` 属性，按钮文本是\"主控台\"而不是\"控制台\"。我需要读取测试脚本，然后根据实际结构修复它。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c71d5013714f4b6abb996bb8","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"path":"astrohub/tools/e2e_v801_full.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1853,"output":436,"cacheRead":116857,"cacheWrite":5561,"totalTokens":124707,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782878856624,"responseId":"msg_dcb0dbc6-3136-4982-bba9-f482611974c2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b102094","parentId":"3c506676","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:08:12.505Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_c71d5013714f4b6abb996bb8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v8.01 E2E 全功能验证脚本\n\n通过 Playwright 模拟真实用户操作，验证所有核心功能模块。\n\nAuthor: 开发工厂\nVersion: v8.01\n\"\"\"\n\nimport asyncio\nimport json\nimport os\nimport time\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom playwright.async_api import async_playwright, Page, expect\n\n# === 配置 ===\nBASE_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:10280\"\nDEVICE_IP = \"192.168.5.72\"\nRESULTS = []\nSCREENSHOT_DIR = Path(\"e2e_screenshots\")\n\ndef log_result(test_name: str, passed: bool, detail: str = \"\"):\n    status = \"[PASS]\" if passed else \"[FAIL]\"\n    RESULTS.append({\"test\": test_name, \"passed\": passed, \"detail\": detail})\n    print(f\"  {status} [{test_name}] {detail}\")\n\nasync def screenshot(page: Page, name: str):\n    SCREENSHOT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    path = SCREENSHOT_DIR / f\"{name}.png\"\n    await page.screenshot(path=str(path), full_page=False)\n\ndef wait_for_user(ms=500):\n    time.sleep(ms / 1000)\n\n# ============================================================\n#  1. 设备发现 & 连接\n# ============================================================\nasync def test_device_discovery_and_connect(page: Page):\n    print(\"\\n=== 1. 设备发现 & 连接 ===\")\n    \n    # 1.1 访问主页\n    await page.goto(BASE_URL, timeout=30000)\n    await page.wait_for_load_state(\"networkidle\")\n    await screenshot(page, \"01_homepage\")\n    log_result(\"首页加载\", True, f\"URL={BASE_URL}\")\n    \n    # 1.2 检查版本号\n    title = await page.title()\n    log_result(\"页面标题\", \"AstroHub\" in title, f\"title={title}\")\n    \n    # 1.3 点击设备页面\n    devices_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"设备\"), [data-page=\"devices\"], .nav-btn:has-text(\"设备\"), text=\"设备\"').first\n    if await devices_btn.count() == 0:\n        # 尝试侧边栏或顶部导航\n        devices_btn = page.locator('[class*=\"nav\"]:has-text(\"设备\"), a:has-text(\"设备\"), li:has-text(\"设备\")').first\n    \n    try:\n        await devices_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"02_devices_page\")\n        log_result(\"设备页面\", True, \"导航到设备页面成功\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"设备页面\", False, f\"导航失败: {e}\")\n        return\n    \n    # 1.4 检查设备列表是否存在\n    try:\n        # 等待设备列表加载\n        await page.wait_for_selector('table, .device-list, .device-card, [class*=\"device\"]', timeout=10000)\n        device_count = await page.locator('table tbody tr, .device-item, .device-card').count()\n        log_result(\"设备列表\", device_count > 0, f\"发现 {device_count} 个设备\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"设备列表\", False, f\"未找到设备: {e}\")\n    \n    # 1.5 检查设备状态（离线/在线/已连接）\n    try:\n        status_el = page.locator('[class*=\"status\"], text=\"已连接\", text=\"在线\", text=\"离线\", text=\"未连接\"').first\n        status_text = await status_el.inner_text() if await status_el.count() > 0 else \"未知\"\n        log_result(\"设备状态显示\", True, f\"状态: {status_text}\")\n    except:\n        log_result(\"设备状态显示\", False, \"未找到状态元素\")\n    \n    # 1.6 连接设备\n    try:\n        # 尝试点击连接按钮\n        connect_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"连接\"), [class*=\"connect\"]:not([class*=\"disconnect\"])').first\n        if await connect_btn.count() == 0:\n            # 尝试点击设备行/卡片来连接\n            connect_btn = page.locator('[class*=\"device\"]:not([class*=\"connected\"]), tr:has-text(\"192.168\")').first\n        \n        if await connect_btn.count() > 0:\n            await connect_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(5000)  # 等待连接完成\n            await screenshot(page, \"03_device_connecting\")\n            \n            # 检查连接成功提示\n            toast = page.locator('[class*=\"toast\"], [class*=\"alert\"], [class*=\"success\"], text=\"已连接\", text=\"连接成功\"').first\n            if await toast.count() > 0:\n\n[417 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782878892505}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c08dedb","parentId":"9b102094","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:08:39.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to fix the test script. I've now seen the page structure:\n\nNavigation buttons (lines 218-228):\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn active\" data-page=\"dashboard\">仪表盘</button>`\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"devices\">设备管理</button>`\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"console\">主控台</button>`\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"observation\">观测计划</button>`\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"advanced\">高级功能</button>`\n\n\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"replay\">回放</button>`\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"settings\">设置</button>`\n\nThe test script is using incorrect selectors—it's referencing \"控制台\" when it should be \"主控台\" for the console button. I need to scan through the test script and update all the navigation button selectors to match the actual page elements. 现在我看到了导航按钮的实际结构，应该用 `data-page` 属性来定位这些元素，而不是用文本选择器。这样更可靠——比如用 `[data-page=\"console\"]` 来定位控制台，`[data-page=\"advanced\"]` 定位高级功能，`[data-page=\"replay\"]` 定位回放功能。\n\n接下来需要检查测试脚本中的其他选择器，确保它们也与页面结构匹配。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，我需要先读取完整的测试脚本，然后根据实际页面结构来修复。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a69d7d053c924918b95f49d0","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":101,"path":"astrohub/tools/e2e_v801_full.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1603,"output":387,"cacheRead":115707,"cacheWrite":8558,"totalTokens":126255,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782878892508,"responseId":"msg_4a310b3d-c0a4-46b3-ad03-21d6a7b0f1a8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"66b688ae","parentId":"7c08dedb","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:08:39.214Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_a69d7d053c924918b95f49d0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                toast_text = await toast.inner_text()\n                log_result(\"设备连接\", True, f\"提示: {toast_text[:50]}\")\n            else:\n                # 检查状态是否变为已连接\n                status_after = await page.locator('text=\"已连接\"').count()\n                log_result(\"设备连接\", status_after > 0, \"连接状态检查\")\n                await screenshot(page, \"03_device_connected\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"设备连接\", False, \"未找到连接按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"设备连接\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n\n# ============================================================\n#  2. WASM 播放 & 码流控制\n# ============================================================\nasync def test_wasm_playback_and_stream(page: Page):\n    print(\"\\n=== 2. WASM 播放 & 码流控制 ===\")\n    \n    # 2.1 导航到控制台/实时播放页面\n    try:\n        console_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"], text=\"控制台\", text=\"实时\", text=\"播放\", text=\"监控\"').first\n        if await console_btn.count() == 0:\n            console_btn = page.locator('a:has-text(\"控制台\"), li:has-text(\"控制台\")').first\n        \n        await console_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"04_console_page\")\n        log_result(\"控制台页面\", True, \"导航成功\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"控制台页面\", False, f\"导航失败: {e}\")\n        return\n    \n    # 2.2 检查播放器容器\n    try:\n        player = page.locator('#player, [class*=\"player\"], [class*=\"video\"], [class*=\"stream\"], video, canvas').first\n        if await player.count() > 0:\n            log_result(\"播放器容器\", True, \"播放器元素存在\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"播放器容器\", False, \"未找到播放器\")\n    except:\n        log_result(\"播放器容器\", False, \"查找失败\")\n    \n    # 2.3 码流切换\n    try:\n        stream_btns = page.locator('button:has-text(\"主码流\"), button:has-text(\"子码流\"), button:has-text(\"第三码流\"), [class*=\"stream\"]:has-text(\"码流\")')\n        stream_count = await stream_btns.count()\n        if stream_count > 0:\n            # 获取当前码流\n            current = await stream_btns.nth(0).inner_text() if stream_count > 0 else \"未知\"\n            \n            # 点击另一个码流\n            if stream_count > 1:\n                await stream_btns.nth(1).click(timeout=5000)\n                await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n                await screenshot(page, \"05_stream_switched\")\n                log_result(\"码流切换\", True, f\"从 {current} 切换\")\n            else:\n                log_result(\"码流切换\", False, \"只有一个码流选项\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"码流切换\", False, \"未找到码流按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"码流切换\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 2.4 截图功能\n    try:\n        capture_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"截图\"), button:has-text(\"拍照\"), [class*=\"capture\"], [class*=\"screenshot\"]').first\n        if await capture_btn.count() > 0:\n            await capture_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"06_screenshot_triggered\")\n            log_result(\"截图功能\", True, \"截图按钮已触发\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"截图功能\", False, \"未找到截图按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"截图功能\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 2.5 录像功能\n    try:\n        record_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"录像\"), button:has-text(\"录制\"), [class*=\"record\"]').first\n        if await record_btn.count() > 0:\n            btn_text = await record_btn.inner_text()\n            # 点击开始录像\n            await record_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"07_recording_started\")\n            log_result(\"录像开始\", True, f\"按钮: {btn_text}\")\n            \n            # 等待几秒后停止\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n            # 再次点击停止\n            await record_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            log_result(\"录像停止\", True, \"录像已停止\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"录像功能\", False, \"未找到录像按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"录像功能\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n\n# ============================================================\n#  3. 高级功能: Function / Speed / Limit\n# ============================================================\nasync def test_advanced_functions(page: Page):\n    print(\"\\n=== 3. 高级功能测试 ===\")\n    \n    # 3.1 导航到高级功能页面\n    try:\n        advanced_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"高级\"), [data-page=\"advanced\"], text=\"高级\", text=\"测试\"').first\n        if await advanced_btn.count() == 0:\n            advanced_btn = page.locator('a:has-text(\"高级\"), li:has-text(\"高级\")').first\n        \n        await advanced_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"08_advanced_page\")\n        log_result(\"高级功能页面\", True, \"导航成功\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"高级功能页面\", False, f\"导航失败: {e}\")\n        return\n    \n    # 3.2 Function 测试 - 设备功能探测\n    try:\n        func_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"功能\"), button:has-text(\"探测\"), [class*=\"function\"], [class*=\"detect\"]').first\n        if await func_btn.count() > 0:\n            await func_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(10000)  # 功能探测需要时间\n            await screenshot(page, \"09_function_test\")\n            \n            # 检查结果\n            result_text = await page.locator('[class*=\"result\"], [class*=\"success\"], [class*=\"fail\"], text=\"通过\", text=\"失败\", text=\"支持\", text=\"不支持\"').first.inner_text() if await page.locator('[class*=\"result\"], text=\"通过\", text=\"失败\"').count() > 0 else \"等待中\"\n            log_result(\"Function 测试\", True, f\"结果: {result_text[:80]}\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"Function 测试\", False, \"未找到功能测试按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"Function 测试\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 3.3 Speed 测试 - 速度测试\n    try:\n        speed_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"速度\"), [class*=\"speed\"]').first\n        if await speed_btn.count() > 0:\n            await speed_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(15000)  # 速度测试需要设备移动\n            await screenshot(page, \"10_speed_test\")\n            \n            # 检查设备是否真的移动了（通过位置变化判断）\n            log_result(\"Speed 测试\", True, \"测试已执行，设备应已移动\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"Speed 测试\", False, \"未找到速度测试按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"Speed 测试\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 3.4 Limit 测试 - 限位测试\n    try:\n        limit_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"限位\"), [class*=\"limit\"]').first\n        if await limit_btn.count() > 0:\n            await limit_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(20000)  # 限位测试需要较长时间\n            await screenshot(page, \"11_limit_test\")\n            \n            # 检查设备是否真的移动了\n            log_result(\"Limit 测试\", True, \"测试已执行，设备应已移动\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"Limit 测试\", False, \"未找到限位测试按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"Limit 测试\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n\n# ============================================================\n#  4. ISAPI 图像控制\n# ============================================================\nasync def test_isapi_image_controls(page: Page):\n    print(\"\\n=== 4. ISAPI 图像控制 ===\")\n    \n    # 4.1 导航到控制台\n    try:\n        console_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"], text=\"控制台\"').first\n        await console_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n    except:\n        log_result(\"ISAPI 控制台\", False, \"导航失败\")\n        return\n    \n    # 4.2 切换到手动模式\n    try:\n        mode_select = page.locator('select:has-text(\"自动\"), select:has-text(\"手动\"), [class*=\"mode\"]').first\n        if await mode_select.count() > 0:\n            # 切换到手动\n            await mode_select.select_option(label=\"手动\", timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"12_manual_mode\")\n            log_result(\"手动模式切换\", True, \"已切换到手动模式\")\n        else:\n            # 尝试按钮方式\n            mode_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"手动\"), button:has-text(\"自动\"), [class*=\"mode\"]').first\n            if await mode_btn.count() > 0:\n                await mode_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n                await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n                log_result(\"手动模式切换\", True, \"模式已切换\")\n            else:\n                log_result(\"手动模式切换\", False, \"未找到模式控制\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"手动模式切换\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n\n[217 more lines in file. Use offset=301 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782878919214}}
{"type":"message","id":"b293cb0c","parentId":"66b688ae","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:09:05.051Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 响应现在我已经看到了完整的导航按钮结构，确认按钮文本是\"主控台\"而不是\"控制台\"。修复测试脚本的关键是：\n\n1. 将 `has-text(\"控制台\")` 改为 `has-text(\"主控台\")`\n2. 将 `has-text(\"高级\")` 改为 `has-text(\"高级功能\")`\n3. 将 `text=\"控制台\"` 改为 `text=\"主控台\"`\n4. 将 `text=\"实时\"`、`text=\"播放\"`、`text=\"监控\"` 从控制台页面选择器中移除（这些是多余的）\n5. 将 `text=\"测试\"` 从高级功能选择器中移除（多余的）\n\n修复思路：\n- 使用 `data-page` 属性定位导航按钮（更可靠）\n- 对于 Control Bar 样式的区域，使用 `[data-page=\"console\"]` 定位主控台\n- 对于高级功能，使用 `[data-page=\"advanced\"]` 定位\n\n现在我需要遍历测试脚本并根据实际页面结构来修复所有选择器。核心修复点：\n\n测试脚本中的错误选择器：\n- `has-text(\"控制台\")` → `[data-page=\"console\"]` (使用 data-page 属性)\n- `has-text(\"高级\")` → `[data-page=\"advanced\"]` \n- `has-text(\"回放\")` → `[data-page=\"replay\"]`\n- `text=\"控制台\"` → 删除（用 data-page 属性替代）\n- `text=\"实时\", text=\"播放\", text=\"监控\"` → 删除多余选择器\n- `text=\"测试\"` → 删除多余选择器\n\n现在我看到主要的测试脚本内容，包含：\n1. 设备发现 & 连接 - 第1个测试\n2. WASM 播放 & 码流控制 - 第2个测试\n3. 高级功能测试 - 第3个测试 (Function/Speed/Limit)\n4. ISAPI 图像控制 - 第4个测试\n5. 回放与录像回放 - 第5个测试\n6. API 直接调用验证 - 第6个测试\n\n我需要修复所有导航按钮的选择器。现在继续读取剩余的测试脚本来全面了解问题。\n\n等待用户指示。继续读取剩余的测试脚本：","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_JEcUBhxbHzhKU8qSYyeb2029","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":120,"offset":301,"path":"astrohub/tools/e2e_v801_full.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":129093,"output":574,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129667,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782878919218,"responseId":"cht000d07c5@dx19f1bdd972329c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a770b461","parentId":"b293cb0c","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:09:05.101Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_JEcUBhxbHzhKU8qSYyeb2029","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    # 4.3 调整光圈 Iris\n    try:\n        iris_slider = page.locator('input[type=\"range\"][class*=\"iris\"], input[type=\"range\"]:has-text(\"光圈\"), [class*=\"iris\"] input[type=\"range\"], input[class*=\"iris\"]').first\n        if await iris_slider.count() == 0:\n            # 尝试其他方式\n            iris_slider = page.locator('text=\"光圈\"').locator('xpath=..').locator('input[type=\"range\"]')\n        \n        if await iris_slider.count() > 0:\n            await iris_slider.fill(\"50\", timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"13_iris_adjusted\")\n            log_result(\"光圈调整\", True, \"光圈已调整\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"光圈调整\", False, \"未找到光圈控制\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"光圈调整\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 4.4 调整快门 Shutter\n    try:\n        shutter_slider = page.locator('input[type=\"range\"][class*=\"shutter\"], input[type=\"range\"]:has-text(\"快门\"), [class*=\"shutter\"] input[type=\"range\"]').first\n        if await shutter_slider.count() > 0:\n            await shutter_slider.fill(\"30\", timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"14_shutter_adjusted\")\n            log_result(\"快门调整\", True, \"快门已调整\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"快门调整\", False, \"未找到快门控制\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"快门调整\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 4.5 调整白平衡 White Balance\n    try:\n        wb_select = page.locator('select[class*=\"whitebalance\"], select[class*=\"wb\"], select:has-text(\"白平衡\")').first\n        if await wb_select.count() > 0:\n            await wb_select.select_option(index=1, timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"15_wb_adjusted\")\n            log_result(\"白平衡调整\", True, \"白平衡已调整\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"白平衡调整\", False, \"未找到白平衡控制\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"白平衡调整\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 4.6 恢复默认\n    try:\n        reset_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"恢复\"), button:has-text(\"默认\"), button:has-text(\"重置\"), [class*=\"reset\"], [class*=\"default\"]').first\n        if await reset_btn.count() > 0:\n            await reset_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"16_settings_reset\")\n            log_result(\"恢复默认\", True, \"设置已恢复默认\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"恢复默认\", False, \"未找到恢复默认按钮\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"恢复默认\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n\n# ============================================================\n#  5. 回放 & 缩略图\n# ============================================================\nasync def test_playback_and_thumbnails(page: Page):\n    print(\"\\n=== 5. 回放 & 缩略图 ===\")\n    \n    # 5.1 导航到回放页面\n    try:\n        replay_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"回放\"), [data-page=\"replay\"], text=\"回放\", text=\"录像回放\"').first\n        if await replay_btn.count() == 0:\n            replay_btn = page.locator('a:has-text(\"回放\"), li:has-text(\"回放\")').first\n        \n        await replay_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"17_replay_page\")\n        log_result(\"回放页面\", True, \"导航成功\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"回放页面\", False, f\"导航失败: {e}\")\n        return\n    \n    # 5.2 检查录像文件列表\n    try:\n        file_list = page.locator('[class*=\"file\"], [class*=\"record\"], tr, .file-item').first\n        if await file_list.count() > 0:\n            count = await page.locator('[class*=\"file\"], [class*=\"record\"], tr').count()\n            log_result(\"录像文件列表\", count > 0, f\"找到 {count} 个文件\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"录像文件列表\", False, \"未找到文件列表\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log_result(\"录像文件列表\", False, f\"异常: {e}\")\n    \n    # 5.3 检查缩略图\n    try:\n        thumbnail = page.locator('img[class*=\"thumb\"], img[class*=\"thumbnail\"], [class*=\"thumbnail\"] img').first\n        if await thumbnail.count() > 0:\n            log_result(\"缩略图\", True, \"缩略图存在\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"缩略图\", False, \"未找到缩略图\")\n    except:\n        log_result(\"缩略图\", False, \"查找失败\")\n\n# ============================================================\n#  6. API 直接验证\n# ============================================================\nasync def test_api_endpoints(page: Page):\n    print(\"\\n=== 6. API 直接验证 ===\")\n    \n    api_tests = [\n        (\"设备列表\", \"/api/v1/devices\"),\n        (\"PTZ 位置\", f\"/api/v1/ptz/{DEVICE_IP}/position\"),\n        (\"图像-光圈\", f\"/api/v1/ptz/{DEVICE_IP}/image/iris\"),\n        (\"图像-快门\", f\"/api/v1/ptz/{DEVICE_IP}/image/shutter\"),\n        (\"图像-白平衡\", f\"/api/v1/ptz/{DEVICE_IP}/image/whitebalance\"),\n        (\"图像-降噪\", f\"/api/v1/ptz/{DEVICE_IP}/image/noisereduce\"),\n    ]\n    \n    for name, endpoint in api_tests:\n        try:\n            response = await page.evaluate(f\"\"\"\n                async () => {{\n                    const r = await fetch('{BASE_URL}{endpoint}');\n                    return {{ status: r.status, ok: r.ok }};\n                }}\n            \"\"\")\n\n[97 more lines in file. Use offset=421 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782878945101}}
