{"type":"message","id":"2660003f","parentId":"b18ba29e","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:13:50.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see that in the console page, the controls are:\n- `#irisLevel` - a select element for iris\n- `#shutterSpeed` - a select element for shutter\n- `#exposureMode` - exposure mode select\n- White balance mode: `#wbMode` probably\n\nSo the test script is looking for sliders but the actual controls are select dropdowns. The test needs to be updated to look for select elements, not input[type=\"range\"] sliders.\n\nI also need to fix the replay page selector. Let me check what the actual replay page structure looks like.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在我看到了。控制台页面中光圈/快门用的是 **select 下拉框**（`#irisLevel`、`#shutterSpeed`），不是滑块。白平衡也是 select（`#wbMode`）。\n\n让我查看回放页面的选择器问题：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6155c4a0fe514e48bf07f050","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub/src/web/index.html\" -Pattern 'data-page=\"replay\"' | Select-Object -First 5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1479,"output":239,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":133313,"totalTokens":135031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782879211414,"responseId":"msg_2867377d-0a36-4961-81fd-d9def19740a7"}}
