{"type":"message","id":"5e6cb75f","parentId":"da18a059","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:14:40.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户反馈测试脚本选择器问题。现在我看到：\n\n1. 光圈/快门/白平衡：实际是 select 元素（`#irisLevel`, `#shutterSpeed`, `#wbMode`），不是滑块\n2. 回放按钮：`data-page=\"replay\"` 存在\n\n测试脚本中的错误：\n- 第303行：光圈用的是 `input[type=\"range\"]`，但实际是 `#irisLevel` select\n- 第320行：快门用的是 `input[type=\"range\"]`，但实际是 `#shutterSpeed` select\n- 第333行：白平衡选择器不对，实际是 `#wbMode`\n- 第365行：回放按钮选择器有语法错误，应该用 `[data-page=\"replay\"]`\n\n我需要修复这些选择器，使用实际的元素 ID。\n\n让我修复测试脚本中的这些选择器。\n\n1. 光圈：`page.locator('select#irisLevel')`\n2. 快门：`page.locator('select#shutterSpeed')`\n3. 白平衡：`page.locator('select#wbMode')`\n4. 回放按钮：`page.locator('[data-page=\"replay\"]')`\n\n让我检查测试脚本中的具体行号并修复。\n现在修复测试脚本：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_961fb468674842ffa9e37c98","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"iris_select = page.locator('select#irisLevel').first\n        await iris_select.select_option(label='光圈值 5', timeout=5000)\n        log_result('光圈调整', True, '已调整到光圈值5')","oldText":"iris_slider = page.locator('input[type=\"range\"][class*=\"iris\"], input[type=\"range\"]:has-text(\"光圈\"), [class*=\"iris\"] input[type=\"range\"], input[class*=\"iris\"]').first\n        if await iris_slider.count() == 0:\n            # 尝试其他方式\n            iris_slider = page.locator('text=\"光圈\"').locator('xpath=..').locator('input[type=\"range\"]')\n        \n        if await iris_slider.count() > 0:\n            await iris_slider.fill(\"50\", timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"13_iris_adjusted\")\n            log_result(\"光圈调整\", True, \"光圈已调整\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"光圈调整\", False, \"未找到光圈控制\")"},{"newText":"shutter_select = page.locator('select#shutterSpeed').first\n        await shutter_select.select_option(label='1/100', timeout=5000)\n        log_result('快门调整', True, '已调整到1/100')","oldText":"shutter_slider = page.locator('input[type=\"range\"][class*=\"shutter\"], input[type=\"range\"]:has-text(\"快门\"), [class*=\"shutter\"] input[type=\"range\"]').first\n        if await shutter_slider.count() > 0:\n            await shutter_slider.fill(\"30\", timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"14_shutter_adjusted\")\n            log_result(\"快门调整\", True, \"快门已调整\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"快门调整\", False, \"未找到快门控制\")"},{"newText":"wb_select = page.locator('select#wbMode').first\n        await wb_select.select_option(index=1, timeout=5000)\n        log_result('白平衡调整', True, '已调整白平衡模式')","oldText":"wb_select = page.locator('select[class*=\"whitebalance\"], select[class*=\"wb\"], select:has-text(\"白平衡\")').first\n        if await wb_select.count() > 0:\n            await wb_select.select_option(index=1, timeout=5000)\n            await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            await screenshot(page, \"15_wb_adjusted\")\n            log_result(\"白平衡调整\", True, \"白平衡已调整\")\n        else:\n            log_result(\"白平衡调整\", False, \"未找到白平衡控制\")"},{"newText":"replay_btn = page.locator('button[data-page=\"replay\"], button:has-text(\"回放\")').first","oldText":"replay_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"回放\"), [data-page=\"replay\"], text=\"回放\", text=\"录像回放\"').first"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tools\\e2e_v801_full.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe issue is that the test script is using `has-text()` which doesn't work with the CSS selector syntax. The actual page has:\n- `<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"replay\">回放</button>`\n\nThe test script is using:\n```python\nreplay_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"回放\"), [data-page=\"replay\"], text=\"回放\", text=\"录像回放\"').first\n```\n\nThis is wrong because `has-text()` doesn't work with comma-separated selectors in Playwright CSS. The correct approach would be to use `data-page` attribute directly or use Playwright's text selector.\n\nLet me fix all the problematic selectors in the test script:\n\n1. Console page navigation (line 121) - use `[data-page=\"console\"]` directly\n2. Advanced page navigation (line 207) - use `[data-page=\"advanced\"]` directly  \n3. Replay page navigation (line 365) - use `[data-page=\"replay\"]` directly\n4. Image controls - the actual elements are:\n   - `#irisLevel` (select)\n   - `#shutterSpeed` (select)\n   - `#wbMode` (select)\n\nLet me fix the test script now.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b4aa6ab8dcb94d34b9aad6d2","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"console_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]').first","oldText":"console_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"]').first"},{"newText":"advanced_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"advanced\"]').first","oldText":"advanced_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"高级\"), [data-page=\"advanced\"], text=\"高级\", text=\"测试\"').first"},{"newText":"replay_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"replay\"]').first","oldText":"replay_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"回放\"), [data-page=\"replay\"], text=\"回放\", text=\"录像回放\"').first"},{"newText":"iris_select = page.locator('#irisLevel').first\n        if await iris_select.count() > 0:\n            await iris_select.select_option(value=\"open\", timeout=5000)","oldText":"iris_slider = page.locator('input[type=\"range\"][class*=\"iris\"], input[type=\"range\"]:has-text(\"光圈\"), [class*=\"iris\"] input[type=\"range\"], input[class*=\"iris\"]').first\n        if await iris_slider.count() == 0:\n            # 尝试其他方式\n            iris_slider = page.locator('text=\"光圈\"').locator('xpath=..').locator('input[type=\"range\"]')\n        \n        if await iris_slider.count() > 0:\n            await iris_slider.fill(\"50\", timeout=5000)"},{"newText":"shutter_select = page.locator('#shutterSpeed').first\n        if await shutter_select.count() > 0:\n            await shutter_select.select_option(value=\"1/100\", timeout=5000)","oldText":"shutter_slider = page.locator('input[type=\"range\"][class*=\"shutter\"], input[type=\"range\"]:has-text(\"快门\"), [class*=\"shutter\"] input[type=\"range\"]').first\n        if await shutter_slider.count() > 0:\n            await shutter_slider.fill(\"30\", timeout=5000)"},{"newText":"wb_select = page.locator('#wbMode').first\n        if await wb_select.count() > 0:\n            await wb_select.select_option(index=1, timeout=5000)","oldText":"wb_select = page.locator('select[class*=\"whitebalance\"], select[class*=\"wb\"], select:has-text(\"白平衡\")').first\n        if await wb_select.count() > 0:\n            await wb_select.select_option(index=1, timeout=5000)"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tools\\e2e_v801_full.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":298,"output":2027,"cacheRead":132387,"cacheWrite":2399,"totalTokens":137111,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782879231197,"responseId":"msg_72e6a352-8ef7-4735-8be4-e1e6bd040a35"}}
