{"type":"message","id":"3820a145","parentId":"a0635f3c","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:15:46.642Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the test script, I can see several issues:\n\n1. Lines 121, 123: `console_btn` - The Chinese text is garbled but it says \"控制台\" (control console), but the actual button text in the HTML is \"主控台\" (main console). So the `has-text(\"控制台\")` won't match.\n\n2. Lines 207, 209: `advanced_btn` - Similarly garbled but says \"高级\" (advanced), the actual button text is \"高级功能\" (advanced function).\n\n3. Lines 273: `console_btn` - Same issue as #1.\n\n4. Lines 303, 311, 319: The iris, shutter, and wb selectors have been updated to use `select#irisLevel`, `select#shutterSpeed`, `select#wbMode` which is correct.\n\n5. Line 346: `replay_btn` - The text is garbled but says \"回放\" which should match the actual button text \"回放\".\n\nThe main issues are:\n- Navigation buttons use wrong text: \"控制台\" vs \"主控台\", \"高级\" vs \"高级功能\"\n- The `has-text()` selector doesn't work well with CSS selectors. In Playwright, `has-text()` is a pseudo-class that works differently.\n\nLooking at the HTML structure from earlier:\n```html\n<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"console\">主控台</button>\n<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"advanced\">高级功能</button>\n<button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"replay\">回放</button>\n```\n\nThe issue is that the test script is using:\n- `button:has-text(\"控制台\")` - wrong text, should be \"主控台\"\n- `button:has-text(\"高级\")` - wrong text, should be \"高级功能\"\n- `button:has-text(\"回放\")` - this one is correct\n\nAnd the `has-text()` pseudo-class in Playwright CSS is different from the `:has-text()` pseudo-class. In Playwright, you should use `text=` prefix or `:text()` pseudo-class.\n\nActually, looking at the Playwright documentation, `:has-text()` is a valid CSS pseudo-class that should work. But the text needs to match exactly or partially.\n\nWait, let me re-read the error from the test run:\n```\n[FAIL] [控制台页面] 导航失败: Locator.count: Unexpected token \"=\" while parsing css selector \"button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"], text=\"控制台\", text=\"实时\", text=\"播放\", text=\"监控\"\". Did you mean to CSS.escape it?\n```\n\nThe error is about parsing the CSS selector. The issue is that the selector has multiple comma-separated parts, and some of them are not valid CSS (like `text=\"控制台\"`). Playwright's `page.locator()` expects a single CSS selector, not a comma-separated list with Playwright-specific syntax mixed in.\n\nSo the fix is to use a single valid CSS selector or use Playwright's locator chaining.\n\nLet me look at the actual code again:\n\nLine 121: `console_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"]').first`\nThis should work if we use just `[data-page=\"console\"]` or `button[data-page=\"console\"]`.\n\nLine 207: `advanced_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"高级\"), [data-page=\"advanced\"]').first`\nThis should work if we use just `[data-page=\"advanced\"]` or `button[data-page=\"advanced\"]`.\n\nLine 346: `replay_btn = page.locator('button[data-page=\"replay\"], button:has-text(\"回放\")').first`\nThis one looks correct already.\n\nActually, looking at the error more carefully:\n```\nUnexpected token \"=\" while parsing css selector \"button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"], text=\"控制台\", text=\"实时\", text=\"播放\", text=\"监控\"\"\n```\n\nThe issue is the `text=\"控制台\"` parts. These are not valid CSS selectors. In Playwright, you should use `text=控制台` (without quotes around the value) or `:text(\"控制台\")`.\n\nSo the fix is to simplify the selectors to just use `[data-page=\"...\"]` attribute selectors.\n\nLet me fix the script:\n\n1. Line 121: Change to `page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]').first`\n2. Line 123: Change to `page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]').first` (same as above, just remove the fallback)\n3. Line 207: Change to `page.locator('[data-page=\"advanced\"]').first`\n4. Line 209: Change to `page.locator('[data-page=\"advanced\"]').first` (same as above)\n5. Line 273: Change to `page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]').first`\n6. Line 346: Already correct, but let me simplify to `page.locator('[data-page=\"replay\"]').first`\n\nActually, looking at the code, lines 123, 209, 348 have fallback logic. Let me just simplify all of them to use the data-page attribute selector.\n看到问题了。测试脚本中的导航按钮选择器有语法错误：\n- `text=\"控制台\"` 不是有效的 CSS 选择器\n- 文本应该是\"主控台\"而不是\"控制台\"\n- 应该简化为 `[data-page=\"...\"]` 属性选择器\n\n修复所有导航按钮：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b35bdcbd4ac844f187a0d17f","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"console_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]').first\n        await console_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"04_console_page\")\n        log_result(\"主控台页面\", True, \"导航成功\")","oldText":"console_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"]').first\n        if await console_btn.count() == 0:\n            console_btn = page.locator('a:has-text(\"控制台\"), li:has-text(\"控制台\")').first\n        \n        await console_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"04_console_page\")\n        log_result(\"控制台页面\", True, \"导航成功\")"},{"newText":"advanced_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"advanced\"]').first\n        await advanced_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"08_advanced_page\")\n        log_result(\"高级功能页面\", True, \"导航成功\")","oldText":"advanced_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"高级\"), [data-page=\"advanced\"]').first\n        if await advanced_btn.count() == 0:\n            advanced_btn = page.locator('a:has-text(\"高级\"), li:has-text(\"高级\")').first\n        \n        await advanced_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"08_advanced_page\")\n        log_result(\"高级功能页面\", True, \"导航成功\")"},{"newText":"console_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]').first\n        await console_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n    except:\n        log_result(\"ISAPI 主控台\", False, \"导航失败\")","oldText":"console_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"控制台\"), [data-page=\"console\"]').first\n        await console_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n    except:\n        log_result(\"ISAPI 控制台\", False, \"导航失败\")"},{"newText":"replay_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"replay\"]').first\n        await replay_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"17_replay_page\")\n        log_result(\"回放页面\", True, \"导航成功\")","oldText":"replay_btn = page.locator('button[data-page=\"replay\"], button:has-text(\"回放\")').first\n        if await replay_btn.count() == 0:\n            replay_btn = page.locator('a:has-text(\"回放\"), li:has-text(\"回放\")').first\n        \n        await replay_btn.click(timeout=5000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        await screenshot(page, \"17_replay_page\")\n        log_result(\"回放页面\", True, \"导航成功\")"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tools\\e2e_v801_full.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2681,"output":2030,"cacheRead":135078,"cacheWrite":2158,"totalTokens":141947,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782879293346,"responseId":"msg_818c70ab-8946-4544-bb27-be0f82cbe149"}}
