{"type":"message","id":"e96bc399","parentId":"51d9e0e8","timestamp":"2026-07-01T04:22:06.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the test results:\n\n1. **Device discovery** - PASS (page load + title)\n   - WARNING on device page navigation due to CSS selector error with `text=\"设备\"` syntax\n\n2. **WASM playback** - PASS (console page navigation, player container, screenshot)\n   - FAIL: stream switch (no button found)\n   - FAIL: recording (GBK encoding error with special character)\n\n3. **Advanced functions** - PASS (page navigation, limit test)\n   - FAIL: Function test (CSS selector error with `text=\"通过\", text=\"失败\"`)\n   - FAIL: Speed test (timeout - wrong element selected: div.ptz-speed instead of button)\n\n4. **ISAPI image controls** - FAIL\n   - Manual mode switch: timeout - wrong element (ptzPresetSelect instead of exposureMode)\n   - The iris/shutter/wb tests - not shown but I fixed them to use correct IDs\n\n5. **Playback** - not shown yet\n\n6. **API tests** - not shown yet\n\nKey issues to fix:\n1. `text=\"设备\"` - invalid CSS selector syntax\n2. `text=\"通过\", text=\"失败\"` - same issue\n3. Speed button selector matches wrong element (div.ptz-speed)\n4. Manual mode selector matches wrong element (ptzPresetSelect)\n5. GBK encoding error with recording\n\nLet me now fix these remaining issues and re-run the test.\n\nFor fix #1: Replace `text=\"设备\"` with just using `[data-page=\"devices\"]` directly\nFor fix #2: Replace `text=\"通过\", text=\"失败\"` with just `[class*=\"result\"]`\nFor fix #3: Add `button` prefix to the speed locator\nFor fix #4: Use `#exposureMode` directly\nFor fix #5: Add try-except with encoding handling\n\nLet me do these fixes now.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，测试完成了。以下是结果汇总：\n\n## 📊 E2E 测试结果（v8.01 修复后）\n\n### ✅ 通过（7项）\n| 项目 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 首页加载 | URL=127.0.0.1:10280 |\n| 页面标题 | title=AstroHub |\n| **主控台页面** | ✅ 已修复（原为\"控制台\"→\"主控台\"） |\n| **高级功能页面