{"type":"message","id":"2aa1778d","parentId":"417312e4","timestamp":"2026-07-01T05:52:00.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板说我别挤牙膏，要自己安排测试、监测进度、反馈结果。我需要：\n1. 修复所有await错误\n2. 运行完整测试\n3. 自动汇报结果\n\n让我先检查脚本中所有可能的await错误，然后一次性修复，再运行完整测试。我需要检查整个脚本，找出所有的 locator 调用，确保正确使用 await。\n\n在 Playwright 中：\n- `page.locator()` - 同步调用，不需要 await\n- `page.is_visible()` - 异步调用，需要 await\n- `locator.is_visible()` - 异步调用，需要 await\n- `locator.click()` - 异步调用，需要 await\n- `locator.first` - 属性，不需要 await\n- `locator.count()` - 异步调用，需要 await\n\n让我一次性修复所有问题。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板说得对。我一次性修复所有 await 问题，然后完整运行测试并汇报结果。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-d3cfde13bcb24cdc8cec1eb82d2ef83b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content astrohub/tools/e2e_v802_full.py -Encoding UTF8 | ForEach-Object { $_ -replace 'await page\\.locator\\(', 'page.locator(' } | Set-Content astrohub/tools/e2e_v802_full.py -Encoding UTF8; Write-Host \"Fixed all await issues\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":145088,"output":269,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145357,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782885075380,"responseId":"cht000db078@dx19f1c3bb2c629bb503"}}
