{"type":"message","id":"8da47a04","parentId":"73b103f4","timestamp":"2026-07-01T10:23:10.256Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full structure of the device table rendering:\n\n1. The table renders with `renderDevices(devices)` function\n2. The actions are built by `buildDeviceActions(d)` function\n3. The connection is a **toggle switch** (not a \"连接\"/\"断开\" button!):\n   ```html\n   <label class=\"switch\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked onchange=\"toggleDeviceConnect('ip', this.checked, 'gateway')\" /><span class=\"slider\"></span></label>\n   ```\n4. Buttons are: 信息 (info), 删除 (delete) or 添加 (add)\n5. There's NO \"连接\" or \"断开\" button - it's a switch toggle instead!\n\nThe test script was searching for `button:has-text('连接')` and `button:has-text('断开')` but the actual device table uses a `<label class=\"switch\">` with a `<input type=\"checkbox\">` for connecting/disconnecting.\n\nThis is why the test was failing - the connect/disconnect mechanism is a toggle switch, not a text button.\n\nAlso, regarding the \"当前路径\" issue - the `input_value()` call returned empty because the input probably loads later via JS.\n\nNow I need to fix the test script to:\n1. Use the switch toggle instead of looking for \"连接\"/\"断开\" buttons\n2. Handle the path input more robustly\n\nLet me also check the `toggleDeviceConnect` function to understand its behavior.\n\nThe `buildDeviceActions` function shows:\n```javascript\nvar switchHtml = '<label class=\"switch\"><input type=\"checkbox\" ' +\n    (isConnected ? 'checked' : '') + ' onchange=\"toggleDeviceConnect(\\'' + d.ip + '\\', this.checked, \\'' + (d.gateway || '') + '\\')\" /><span class=\"slider\"></span></label>';\nbtns.push(switchHtml);\n```\n\nAnd at line 1248:\n```javascript\nwindow.toggleDeviceConnect = function(ip, checked, gateway) {\n    if (checked) {\n        var d = allDevices.find(function(dev) { return dev.ip === ip; });\n        if (d && d.has_credentials) {\n```\n\nSo to connect/disconnect:\n1. Find the switch checkbox in the table row\n2. Click it to toggle\n3. The checkbox state (checked/unchecked) indicates connection status\n\nFor the test, I should:\n1. Find the checkbox/label.switch in the device table\n2. If not checked, click it to connect\n3. After some time, click it again to disconnect\n\nLet me also fix the path issue - the `input_value()` might fail if the input is populated via JavaScript after page load.\n\nI'll update the test script now.我先搞清楚结构。搜索 buildDeviceActions 和按钮文本：","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CNoay3gT0hBHab5UEZz20874","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1227,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":160194,"output":698,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":160892,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782901332605,"responseId":"cht000d071c@dx19f1d33d0122872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecba1189","parentId":"8da47a04","timestamp":"2026-07-01T10:23:10.308Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_CNoay3gT0hBHab5UEZz20874","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function buildDeviceActions(d) {\r\n            var btns = [];\r\n            var isConnected = window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip === d.ip;\r\n            // v6.35: 连接开关(只有一个设备可连接)\r\n            var switchHtml = '<label class=\"switch\"><input type=\"checkbox\" ' +\r\n                (isConnected ? 'checked' : '') + ' onchange=\"toggleDeviceConnect(\\'' + d.ip + '\\', this.checked, \\'' + (d.gateway || '') + '\\')\" /><span class=\"slider\"></span></label>';\r\n            btns.push(switchHtml);\r\n            // v6.35: 信息按钮(弹窗显示设备详情)\r\n            btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"showDeviceInfoModal(\\'' + d.ip + '\\')\">信息</button>');\r\n            // Add modify IP button for all devices\r\n            // v7.15: 添加/删除按钮交互式\r\n            var isAdded = d.has_credentials;\r\n            if (isAdded) {\r\n                btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"deleteDevice(\\'' + (d.mac || d.ip) + '\\')\">删除</button>');\r\n            } else {\r\n                btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"quickAddDevice(\\'' + d.ip + '\\', \\'' + (d.gateway || '') + '\\')\">添加</button>');\r\n            }\r\n            return '<div class=\"actions\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px\">' + btns.join('') + '</div>';\r\n        }\r\n        // v6.35: 切换设备连接状态\r\n        window.toggleDeviceConnect = function(ip, checked, gateway) {\r\n            if (checked) {\r\n                var d = allDevices.find(function(dev) { return dev.ip === ip; });\r\n                if (d && d.has_credentials) {\r\n                    connectDevice(ip);\r\n                } else {\r\n                    showQuickAddModal(ip, gateway);\r\n                }\r\n            } else {\r\n                disconnectDevice(ip);\r\n\n[1619 more lines in file. Use offset=1257 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782901390308}}
