{"type":"message","id":"521f65c7","parentId":"d83cf1b9","timestamp":"2026-07-01T10:47:14.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"复盘更新记忆\" (review and update memory). I've already written a comprehensive memory file for today (2026-07-01) that includes:\n\n1. v8.02 completion summary\n2. Gateway fix details\n3. E2E test script refactor\n4. Version update\n5. Detailed lessons learned from today's work\n6. Important files to keep\n7. Start and test commands\n\nThis is a good comprehensive review of today's work. The user is asking me to do a retrospective and update the memory, which I've done. The memory file now contains:\n- Key technical lessons about Playwright\n- Lessons about understanding UI structure before writing tests\n\n\n- Playwright API usage patterns\n- Edit tool pitfalls to avoid\n- GBK encoding issues\n- Modal blocking concerns\n- Files I should preserve\n- Start and test commands\n\nI should confirm to the user that the review is complete and summarize what I've recorded.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **复盘完成，记忆已更新。**\n\n**已记录的核心教训（7条）**：\n1. Playwright CSS选择器语法错误\n2. **先搞清楚结构再写脚本**（被纠正后重点记录）\n3. 设备表格连接机制（开关checkbox）\n4. Playwright API同步/异步混用\n5. 编辑工具多块交叉失败\n6. GBK编码emoji报错\n7. 回放modal阻塞导航\n\n**测试脚本**：`astrohub/tools/e2e_v802_full.py`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":3078,"output":326,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":189712,"totalTokens":193116,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782902808144,"responseId":"msg_fe660df4-012e-4668-9df5-d31c61c591d0"}}
